('Finansman Tüccar Pazarlarında Hesabımı Ne Kadar Süreyle Pasif Tutmam Uygundur?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Finanse Tüccar Pazarları''ndaki 30 Günlük Faaliyet Yokluğu Politikası, hesabınızda 30 takvim günü boyunca hiçbir faaliyet yapılmadığı takdirde, bir e-posta gönderileceğini belirten firma kılavuzudur; bu, sözleşme ihlali olarak kabul edilir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu politikanın amacı, maksimum kaynakların kullanılmasını sağlamak ve tüm saygıdeğer müşterilerimize mükemmel hizmet sunmaktır. Tüm pasif hesaplara yönelik kısıtlayıcı önlemler uygulayarak, Finanse Tüccar Pazarları, tüm aşamalar için simüle edilmiş ticaret hesabını otomatik olarak sonlandırma hakkına sahiptir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "İstisnalar:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tatil/İzin veya yaşam olaylarının 30 gün boyunca ticaret faaliyetlerini kesintiye uğratabileceğini kabul ederek, Finanse Tüccar Pazarları esneklik sunmaktadır. Müşteriler, planlı yoklukları hakkında önceden bildirimde bulunurlarsa, 30 günlük faaliyet yokluğu kuralına istisnalar verilebilir; bu, trajik bir durum olmadıkça, mümkünse önceden yapılmalıdır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Esasen, 30 günlük hareketsizlik politikası, Fonlu Trader Pazarlarının kaynakları verimli bir şekilde yönetmesine olanak tanırken, kişisel nedenlerden dolayı geçici hareketsizlik dönemleri yaşayabilecek müşterilere de uyum sağlamaktadır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'finanse-tüccar-pazarlarında-hesabımı-ne-kadar-süreyle-aktif-dışı-bırakmam-uygun', 'Finansman Tüccar Pazarlarında Hesabımı Ne Kadar Süreyle Pasif Tutmam Uygundur?', '30 Günlük Pasiflik Politikası, Funded Trader Markets''te, hesabınızda 30 ardışık gün boyunca herhangi bir işlem yapılmadığında geçerli olan firma kılavuzudur...', 563, 'tr', 125),
('Wie lange ist es zulässig, mein Konto bei Funded Trader Markets inaktiv zu halten?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "30-Tage Inaktivitätsrichtlinie bei Funded Trader Markets, die Unternehmensrichtlinie besagt, dass, wenn in Ihrem Konto 30 aufeinanderfolgende Kalendertage keine Aktivität erfolgt, eine E-Mail als Vertragsverletzung versendet wird.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Zweck dieser Richtlinie ist es, sicherzustellen, dass maximale Ressourcen genutzt werden und exzellenter Service für alle unsere respektvollen Kunden aufrechterhalten wird. Durch die Umsetzung restriktiver Maßnahmen gegenüber allen inaktiven Konten hat Funded Trader Markets das Recht, das simulierte Handelskonto für alle Phasen automatisch zu kündigen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ausnahmen:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Da erkannt wird, dass Urlaube/Ferien oder Lebensereignisse 30 Tage andauern können und den Handelsaktivitäten schaden können, bietet Funded Trader Markets Flexibilität. Wenn Kunden im Voraus über geplante Abwesenheiten informieren, können Ausnahmen von der 30-Tage-Inaktivitätsregel gewährt werden, vorzugsweise im Voraus, wenn nicht tragisch.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Im Wesentlichen ermöglicht die 30-tägige Inaktivitätsrichtlinie den Funded Trader Markets, Ressourcen effizient zu verwalten, während sie Kunden berücksichtigen, die aufgrund persönlicher Gründe vorübergehende Phasen der Inaktivität erleben können.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'fuer-wie-lange-ist-es-erlaubt-mein-konto-bei-funded-trader-markets-inaktiv-zu-lassen', 'Wie lange ist es zulässig, mein Konto bei Funded Trader Markets inaktiv zu halten?', '30-Tage-Inaktivitätsrichtlinie bei Funded Trader Markets, die Unternehmensrichtlinie, die besagt, dass, wenn in Ihrem Konto 30 aufeinanderfolgende Tage lang keine Aktivitäten stattfinden...', 564, 'de', 125),
('ما هي المدة المسموح بها لترك حسابي غير نشط في أسواق المتداولين الممولين؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "سياسة عدم النشاط لمدة 30 يومًا في أسواق المتداولين الممولين، هي إرشادات الشركة التي تنص على أنه إذا لم يكن هناك أي نشاط في حسابك لمدة 30 يومًا تقويميًا متتاليًا، سيتم إرسال بريد إلكتروني كخرق لشرط العقد.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "الغرض من هذه السياسة هو ضمان استخدام الموارد بشكل أقصى والحفاظ على خدمة ممتازة لجميع عملائنا المحترمين. من خلال تنفيذ تدابير تقييدية تجاه جميع الحسابات غير النشطة، فإن أسواق المتداولين الممولين لها الحق في إنهاء حساب التداول المحاكي تلقائيًا لجميع المراحل.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "استثناءات:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مع الاعتراف بأن العطلات/الإجازات، أو الأحداث الحياتية قد تحدث لمدة 30 يومًا، مما قد يعطل أنشطة التداول. تقدم أسواق المتداولين الممولين مرونة. إذا قام العملاء بإخطار مسبق عن الغيابات المخطط لها، قد يتم منح استثناءات لقواعد عدم النشاط لمدة 30 يومًا، ويفضل أن يكون ذلك مسبقًا إذا لم يكن هناك ظرف طارئ.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "بشكل أساسي، تسمح سياسة عدم النشاط لمدة 30 يومًا لشركة Funded Trader Markets بإدارة الموارد بكفاءة مع تلبية احتياجات العملاء الذين قد يواجهون فترات مؤقتة من عدم النشاط لأسباب شخصية.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'لِمَدةٍ طَوِيلَةٍ يُسمَح لي بِتَرك حِسابي غَيْر نشِط في أسواق المتداولين المُمَوَّلين؟', 'ما هي المدة المسموح بها لترك حسابي غير نشط في أسواق المتداولين الممولين؟', 'سياسة عدم النشاط لمدة 30 يومًا في أسواق المتداولين الممولين، وهي إرشادات الشركة التي تنص على أنه إذا لم يكن هناك أي نشاط في حسابك لمدة 30 يومًا متتالية...', 565, 'ar', 125),
('Berapa lama ia dibenarkan untuk membiarkan akaun saya tidak aktif di Funded Trader Markets?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dasar Ketidakaktifan 30-Hari di Funded Trader Markets, garis panduan firma yang menyatakan bahawa jika tiada aktiviti dilakukan dalam akaun anda selama 30 hari kalendar berturut-turut, satu emel akan dihantar sebagai pelanggaran kontrak.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tujuan dasar ini adalah untuk memastikan sumber yang maksimum digunakan dan mengekalkan perkhidmatan yang cemerlang kepada semua pelanggan kami yang dihormati. Dengan melaksanakan langkah-langkah ketat terhadap semua akaun tidak aktif, oleh itu Funded Trader Markets berhak untuk secara automatik menamatkan akaun perdagangan simulasi untuk semua fasa.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengecualian:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Menyedari bahawa percutian / Cuti, atau peristiwa kehidupan mungkin berlaku selama 30 hari, boleh mengganggu aktiviti perdagangan. Funded Trader Markets menawarkan fleksibiliti. Jika pelanggan memberi notis awal tentang ketidakhadiran yang dirancang, pengecualian kepada peraturan ketidakaktifan 30-hari mungkin diberikan, lebih baik jika dilakukan lebih awal jika tidak tragis.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pada dasarnya, polisi ketidakaktifan selama 30 hari membolehkan Funded Trader Markets menguruskan sumber dengan cekap sambil memenuhi keperluan pelanggan yang mungkin mengalami tempoh ketidakaktifan sementara disebabkan oleh alasan peribadi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'untuk-seberapa-lama-adalah-dibolehkan-untuk-menyimpan-akun-saya-tidak-aktif-di-pasar-pedagang-yang-dibiayai', 'Berapa lama ia dibenarkan untuk membiarkan akaun saya tidak aktif di Funded Trader Markets?', 'Dasar Ketidakaktifan 30-Hari di Funded Trader Markets, garis panduan firma yang menyatakan bahawa jika tiada aktiviti dilakukan dalam akaun anda selama 30 hari berturut-turut...', 566, 'ms', 125),
('What Requirements Must Be Met to Merge My Accounts At Funded Trader Markets?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "You can merge your simulated funded accounts up to a maximum of ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "$200,000.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " Here are some examples:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "1 x $100k account + 1 x $100k account", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "1 x $100k account + 2 x $50k accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "2 x $25k accounts + 3 x $50k accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "1 x $100k account + 1 x $50k account + 2 x $25k accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Any combination that does not exceed the $200,000 maximum allocation is allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Criteria for Merging:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "1 – Same Program Requirement:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "All accounts must be from the same program.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Examples:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 8, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Any Standard (Simulated Funded) account can only be merged with another Standard (Simulated Funded) account, provided the total does not exceed $200,000.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Any Speed (Simulated Funded) account can only be merged with another Speed (Simulated Funded) account, provided the total does not exceed $200,000.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "2 – All accounts must be at the initial balance at the time of the Merge request.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "This applies to both fresh, non-traded accounts and traded accounts that have returned to the initial balance after a payout request.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "3- Merge does not apply to Scaled-Up Accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Accounts that have been scaled up are not eligible for merging.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "4 – Accounts still in challenge phases cannot be merged. Instant Funding Accounts cannot be merged. 1-step Accounts cannot be merged.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The accounts to be merged must be on the same trading platform. If the accounts are on different platforms, you must first request a ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"id": "68d135c7684da9601534a28e", "type": "link", "fields": {"url": "https://fundedtradermarkets.com/faq/can-i-switch-my-account-between-offered-trading-platforms/", "newTab": true, "linkType": "custom"}, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 3, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Platform Switch", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " (subject to Platform Switch Criteria).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'what-requirements-must-be-met-to-merge-my-accounts-at-funded-trader-markets', 'What Requirements Must Be Met to Merge My Accounts At Funded Trader Markets?', 'You can merge your simulated funded accounts up to a maximum of $200,000. Here are some examples: 1 x $100k account + 1 x $100k account1 x $100k account...', 569, 'en', 124),
('Welche Anforderungen müssen erfüllt sein, um meine Konten bei Funded Trader Markets zusammenzuführen?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Sie können Ihre simulierten finanzierten Konten bis zu einem Maximum von", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "$200,000.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hier sind einige Beispiele:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "1 x $100k Konto + 1 x $100k Konto", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "1 x $100k Konto + 2 x $50k Konten", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "2 x $25k Konten + 3 x $50k Konten", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "1 x $100k Konto + 1 x $50k Konto + 2 x $25k Konten", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jede Kombination, die das maximale Kontingent von $200.000 nicht überschreitet, ist erlaubt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Kriterien für die Zusammenführung:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "1 – Anforderung an dasselbe Programm:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Alle Konten müssen aus demselben Programm stammen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiele:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 8, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Jedes Standard (Simuliertes Finanzierungs-) Konto kann nur mit einem anderen Standard (Simuliertes Finanzierungs-) Konto zusammengelegt werden, vorausgesetzt, die Gesamtsumme überschreitet nicht 200.000 $.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Jedes Speed (Simuliertes Finanzierungs-) Konto kann nur mit einem anderen Speed (Simuliertes Finanzierungs-) Konto zusammengelegt werden, vorausgesetzt, die Gesamtsumme überschreitet nicht 200.000 $.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "2 – Alle Konten müssen zum Zeitpunkt der Zusammenlegungsanfrage den Anfangsbestand aufweisen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dies gilt sowohl für frische, nicht gehan