('Am I Reinstated/Compensated if My Trading Account is Compromised?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Funded Trader Markets is not responsible for your account(s) getting hacked, it is your responsibility to protect your account credentials at all costs.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Please ensure your account credentials are kept safe from anyone to prevent such an event from happening.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "We will not reinstate accounts that have been exposed, shared with a third party, or lost due to hacking.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Immediate Action", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": If you suspect your account has been compromised, contact our team immediately and we will happily help to change your password to secure your simulated trading account.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Important Note", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Account reinstatements are not considered. It is e