('Hesap Marjı Kuralları, Mücadelem ve Fonlu Hesabım için nasıl uygulanır?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Marjin Çağrısı kuralı, tüm Programlar/Hesaplar için geçerlidir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Funded Trader Markets''teki tüm Değerlendirme ve Simüle Edilmiş Fonlu Hesaplar için özel marjin kuralları şunlardır:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Marjin Çağrısı Seviyesi – %110", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Marjin seviyeniz %110''a ulaştığında, bir Marjin Çağrısı etkinleştirilir. Bu noktada, yeni işlemler açmanız kısıtlanacaktır. Bu, açık pozisyonlarınızın kritik bir risk seviyesine yaklaşmakta olduğunu belirten bir erken uyarıdır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Stop Out Seviyesi – %100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer marj seviyesi %100''e veya altına düşerse, otomatik olarak tüm açık pozisyonlarınızın kapatılacağı bir Stop Out başlatılır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Marj Seviyesi Nasıl Hesaplanır?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Marj Seviyesi % = (Özsermaye / Kullanılan Marj) * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Önemli Notlar:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Risk Yönetimi:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Ticaret tarzınıza uygun etkili risk yönetimi stratejileri kullanın ve hesabınızdaki marj çağrılarını önlemek için zarar durdurma emirleri belirleyin.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Marj Mevcudiyeti", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Mevcut marj, hesabınızdaki mevcut bakiyeye ve işlem seviyesinin özkaydına bağlıdır. Marj %, kârda olduğunuzda artar ve zarar durumunda azalır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Gerekirse marj kuralı hakkında daha fazla netlik için, lütfen web sitesi aracılığıyla veya support@fundedtradermarkets.com adresine e-posta göndererek destekle iletişime geçin.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'hesap-margini-kurallari-benim-meydan-okumama-ve-finanse-edilen-hesabima-nasil-uygulanir', 'Hesap Marjı Kuralları, Mücadelem ve Fonlu Hesabım için nasıl uygulanır?', 'Margin Call kuralı, tüm Programlar/Hesaplar için geçerlidir. İşte Fu''daki tüm Değerlendirme ve Simüle Edilmiş Fonlu Hesaplar için özel marj kuralları.', 676, 'tr', 115),
('Wie gelten die Kontomarginregeln für meine Herausforderung und mein finanziertes Konto?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Die Margin Call-Regel gilt für alle Arten von Programmen/Konten", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hier sind die spezifischen Margin-Regeln für alle Bewertungs- und simulierten finanzierten Konten bei Funded Trader Markets:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Margin Call Niveau – 110%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Ihr Margin-Niveau 110% erreicht, wird ein Margin Call aktiviert. Zu diesem Zeitpunkt sind Sie daran gehindert, neue Trades zu eröffnen. Dies dient als frühe Warnung, dass Ihre offenen Positionen sich einem kritischen Risikoniveau nähern.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Stop Out Level – 100%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn der Margin-Level auf 100% oder darunter fällt, wird ein Stop Out eingeleitet, der zur automatischen Schließung aller Ihrer offenen Positionen führt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wie wird der Margin-Level berechnet?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Margin Level % = (Eigenkapital / Verwendeter Margin) * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wichtige Hinweise:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Risikomanagement:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Verwenden Sie effektive Risikomanagementstrategien, die zu Ihrem Handelsstil passen, und setzen Sie Stop-Loss-Orders, um Margin-Calls auf Ihrem Konto zu vermeiden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Verfügbarkeit von Margin", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Die verfügbare Marge hängt vom aktuellen Kontostand ab, plus dem Eigenkapital des Handelsniveaus. Der Margin-% steigt, wenn ein Gewinn erzielt wird, und sinkt, wenn ein Drawdown auftritt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Für mehr Klarheit über die Margin-Regel, falls erforderlich, können Sie sich gerne über die Website oder per E-Mail an support@fundedtradermarkets.com an den Support wenden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'wie-gelten-die-margin-regeln-für-meine-herausforderung-und-mein-finanziertes-konto', 'Wie gelten die Kontomarginregeln für meine Herausforderung und mein finanziertes Konto?', 'Die Margin Call-Regel gilt für alle Arten von Programmen/Konten. Hier sind die spezifischen Margin-Regeln für alle Bewertungs- und simulierten finanzierten Konten bei Fu...', 677, 'de', 115),
('كيف تنطبق قواعد هامش الحساب على تحدي وحساب ممول الخاص بي؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "تنطبق قاعدة طلب الهامش على جميع أنواع البرامج / الحسابات", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إليك القواعد المحددة للهامش لجميع حسابات التقييم والحسابات الممولة المحاكاة في أسواق المتداولين الممولين:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مستوى طلب الهامش - 110%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "عندما يصل مستوى الهامش الخاص بك إلى 110%، يتم تفعيل طلب الهامش. في هذه المرحلة، سيتم تقييدك من فتح صفقات جديدة. وهذا بمثابة تحذير مبكر، يشير إلى أن مراكزك المفتوحة تقترب من مستوى خطر حرج.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مستوى الإيقاف - 100%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا انخفض مستوى الهامش إلى 100% أو أقل، يتم بدء الإيقاف التلقائي مما يؤدي إلى إغلاق جميع مراكزك المفتوحة تلقائيًا.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "كيف يتم حساب مستوى الهامش؟", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مستوى الهامش % = (الملكية / الهامش المستخدم) * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "ملاحظات هامة:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إدارة المخاطر:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "استخدم استراتيجيات إدارة المخاطر الفعالة التي تناسب أسلوب تداولك وقم بتحديد نقاط وقف الخسارة لتجنب طلبات الهامش على حسابك.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "توفر الهامش", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": يعتمد الهامش المتاح على الرصيد الحالي لحسابك، بالإضافة إلى حقوق الملكية لمستوى التداول. يزيد % الهامش عند تحقيق الربح، وينخفض عند الخسارة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "للمزيد من التوضيح حول قاعدة الهامش إذا لزم الأمر، لا تتردد في الاتصال بالدعم عبر الموقع الإلكتروني أو عبر البريد الإلكتروني support@fundedtradermarkets.com", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'كيف تنطبق قواعد هامش الحساب على تحدي وحساب ممول الخاص بي؟', 'كيف تنطبق قواعد هامش الحساب على تحدي وحساب ممول الخاص بي؟', 'تنطبق قاعدة طلب الهامش على جميع أنواع البرامج/الحسابات. إليك القواعد المحددة للهامش لجميع حسابات التقييم والحسابات الممولة المحاكاة في Fu...', 678, 'ar', 115),
('Bagaimana Peraturan Margin Akaun terpakai kepada Cabaran dan Akaun Dibiayai saya?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Margin Call terpakai untuk semua jenis Program/Akaun", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Berikut adalah peraturan margin khusus untuk semua Akaun Penilaian dan Akaun Simulasi yang Dibiayai di Funded Trader Markets:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tahap Margin Call – 110%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Apabila tahap margin anda mencapai 110%, Margin Call diaktifkan. Pada ketika ini, anda akan dihadkan daripada membuka perdagangan baru. Ini berfungsi sebagai amaran awal, menunjukkan bahawa kedudukan terbuka anda hampir mencapai tahap risiko kritikal.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tahap Henti Keluar – 100%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika tahap margin jatuh kepada 100% atau lebih rendah, Henti Keluar akan dimulakan yang akan mengakibatkan penutupan automatik semua posisi terbuka anda.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bagaimana Tahap Margin Dihitung?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tahap Margin % = (Ekuiti / Margin Digunakan) * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Nota Penting:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengurusan Risiko:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Gunakan strategi pengurusan risiko yang berkesan yang sesuai dengan gaya perdagangan anda dan tetapkan had kerugian untuk mengelakkan panggilan margin pada akaun anda.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ketersediaan Margin", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Margin yang tersedia bergantung pada baki semasa akaun anda, ditambah dengan ekuiti tahap perdagangan. Margin % meningkat apabila dalam keuntungan, dan menurun apabila dalam kerugian.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "directio