('Are There Any Limitations On Certain Trading Practices at Funded Trader Markets?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "At Funded Trader Markets, we empower traders to choose their trading styles and strategies without restrictions. However, it is crucial to follow our guidelines and avoid activities that exploit our", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "systems or violate fair trading practices. The following actions are strictly prohibited:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Using Manipulative Software or Techniques", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Employing software, AI, ultra-high-speed techniques, or mass data entry methods that manipulate or unfairly advantage your use of our systems is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Non-Standard Trading Practices", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in trading practices that deviate from typical forex or financial market trading, or that could cause financial or other harm to the provider.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Using External or Slow Data Feeds", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Executing trades with external or slow data feeds.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Exploiting Service Errors", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Using trading strategies that take advantage of errors in our services, such as price display errors or delayed updates.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Manipulative Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in manipulative trades, such as entering simultaneous opposite positions, either individually or in collaboration with others.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hedging Across Accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Hedging between accounts with other evaluation firms similar to Funded Trader Markets", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Account Management Services", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "All accounts in our challenges must be traded exclusively by the account owner once a phase is completed. Any deviation from this rule will be considered a violation.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Additionally, only one trader per household and IP address is allowed. Breaching this rule will result in the termination of all accounts involved.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Prohibited Trading Practices", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Group Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Group trading and copying trades from others, as well as coordinating and reverse trading with others, are not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "High-Frequency Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in high-frequency trading, which involves trading large volumes of positions at very high speeds, is prohibited.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "News Scalping", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Rapidly opening and closing multiple positions within seconds around high-impact news releases (e.g., FOMC, NFP, CPI) to exploit market feeds is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Arbitrage Trading: Any form of arbitrage trading, including reverse and latency arbitrage, is strictly prohibited.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Multi-Account Reverse Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Reverse trading across multiple accounts, especially around events like FOMC, where you hedge positions across different evaluation firms, is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Tick Scalping", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Scalping in ticks, which involves opening and closing large position sizes in milliseconds, is prohibited as it cannot be mirrored live.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Internal Reverse Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Engaging in reverse trading within Funded Trader Market’s internal accounts is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Copying Trades", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Group Hedging", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Coordinating opposing positions across one or multiple evaluation firms to manipulate risk is strictly prohibited.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Account Management Services", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Purchasing or providing account management services or using evaluation firm passing services is not allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Account Sharing", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Sharing account information or allowing someone else to pass an account on your behalf will result in account termination.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Mirroring Trades", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": It is not allowed to mirror trades from another trader or group of traders across multiple accounts.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Note", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": If any trader is found engaging in any of the prohibited practices, we reserve the right to close the account and forfeit any associated payout without a refund.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'are-there-any-limitations-on-certain-trading-practices-at-funded-trader-markets', 'Are There Any Limitations On Certain Trading Practices at Funded Trader Markets?', 'At Funded Trader Markets, we empower traders to choose their trading styles and strategies without restrictions. However, it is crucial to follow our gu...', 759, 'en', 109),
('Fonlanan Ticaret Pazarlarında Belirli Ticaret Uygulamalarında Herhangi Bir Sınırlama Var Mı?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Funded Trader Markets''te, trader''ların ticaret stillerini ve stratejilerini kısıtlama olmaksızın seçmelerine olanak tanıyoruz. Ancak, yönergelerimize uymak ve sistemlerimizi istismar eden veya adil ticaret uygulamalarını ihlal eden faaliyetlerden kaçınmak çok önemlidir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Aşağıdaki eylemler kesinlikle yasaktır:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Manipülatif Yazılım veya Teknikler Kullanmak", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Yazılım, yapay zeka, ultra yüksek hızlı teknikler veya sistemlerimizi manipüle eden veya kullanımınıza haksız avantaj sağlayan toplu veri girişi yöntemleri kullanmak yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Standart Dışı Ticaret Uygulamaları", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Ticaret uygulamalarının tipik forex veya finansal piyasa ticaretinden sapması veya sağlayıcıya finansal veya başka bir zarar verebilecek uygulamalarla ilgilenmek.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Dış veya Yavaş Veri Akışları Kullanma", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Dış veya yavaş veri akışlarıyla işlemler gerçekleştirmek.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hizmet Hatalarından Yararlanma", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hizmetlerimizdeki hatalardan, örneğin fiyat gösterim hataları veya gecikmeli güncellemeler gibi, yararlanan ticaret stratejileri kullanma.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Manipülatif Ticaret", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Bireysel olarak veya başkalarıyla işbirliği içinde, aynı anda zıt pozisyonlara girme gibi manipülatif işlemlere katılma.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hesaplar Arası Koruma", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hesaplar arasında Funded Trader Markets''a benzer diğer değerlendirme firmaları ile koruma", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hesap Yönetim Hizmetleri", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Zorluklarımızdaki tüm hesaplar, bir aşama tamamlandıktan sonra yalnızca hesap sahibi tarafından işlem görmelidir. Bu kuraldan herhangi bir sapma ihlal olarak kabul edilecektir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Ayrıca, her hane ve IP adresi için yalnızca bir tüccara izin verilmektedir. Bu kuralın ihlali, ilgili tüm hesapların kapatılmasına neden olacaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Yasaklı Ticaret Uygulamaları", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Grup Ticaret", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Grup ticareti ve başkalarından ticaret kopyalamak, başkalarıyla koordinasyon sağlamak ve ters ticaret yapmak yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Yüksek Frekanslı Ticaret", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Yüksek frekanslı ticaret yapmak, çok yüksek hızlarda büyük hacimlerde pozisyonlar ticareti yapmayı içerir ve yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Haber Scalping", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Yüksek etkili haber yayınları (örneğin, FOMC, NFP, CPI) etrafında saniyeler içinde birden fazla pozisyonu hızlıca açıp kapamak, piyasa verilerinden yararlanmak için yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Arbitraj Ticareti: Herhangi bir arbitraj ticareti biçimi, ters ve gecikme arbitrajı dahil, kesinlikle yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Çoklu Hesap Ters Ticaret", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Özellikle FOMC gibi etkinlikler etrafında, farklı değerlendirme firmaları arasında pozisyonları hedge ettiğinizde, birden fazla hesapta ters ticaret yapmak yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Tick Scalping", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Tırtıl ticareti, büyük pozisyon boyutlarını milisaniyeler içinde açıp kapamayı içeren bir işlem olup, canlı olarak yansıtılamadığı için yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "İçsel Ters Ticaret", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Fonlu Trader Pazarının iç hesaplarında ters ticaret yapmak yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ticaretleri Kopyalama", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Grup Hedging", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Bir veya birden fazla değerlendirme firması arasında karşıt pozisyonları koordine ederek riski manipüle etmek kesinlikle yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hesap Yönetim Hizmetleri", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Hesap yönetim hizmetleri satın almak veya sağlamak ya da değerlendirme firması geçiş hizmetlerini kullanmak yasaklanmıştır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hesap Paylaşımı", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hesap bilgilerini paylaşmak veya bir başkasının hesabı sizin adınıza kullanmasına izin vermek hesap kapatılmasına neden olacaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Aynalama İşlemleri", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Başka bir yatırımcıdan veya bir grup yatırımcıdan işlemleri birden fazla hesap üzerinden aynalamak yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Not", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Herhangi bir tüccarın yasaklı uygulamalardan herhangi birini gerçekleştirdiği tespit edilirse, hesabı kapatma ve ilgili ödemeyi iade olmaksızın el koyma hakkını saklı tutarız.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'finanse tüccar pazarlarında belirli ticaret uygulamalarıyla ilgili herhangi bir kısıtlama var mı?', 'Fonlanan Ticaret Pazarlarında Belirli Ticaret Uygulamalarında Herhangi Bir Sınırlama Var Mı?', 'Funded Trader Markets''ta, trader''ların ticaret stillerini ve stratejilerini kısıtlama olmaksızın seçmelerine olanak tanıyoruz. Ancak, kurallarımıza uymak son derece önemlidir...', 760, 'tr', 109),
('Gibt es Einschränkungen bei bestimmten Handelspraktiken an den Märkten für finanzierte Händler?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bei Funded Trader Markets ermöglichen wir Händlern, ihre Handelsstile und -strategien ohne Einschränkungen zu wählen. Es ist jedoch entscheidend, unsere Richtlinien zu befolgen und Aktivitäten zu vermeiden, die unsere", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Systeme ausnutzen oder faire Handelspraktiken verletzen. Die folgenden Handlungen sind strengstens untersagt:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Verwendung manipulativer Software oder Techniken", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Der Einsatz von Software, KI, ultraschnellen Techniken oder Methoden zur Massendateneingabe, die Ihre Nutzung unserer Systeme manipulieren oder unfair begünstigen, ist nicht erlaubt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Nicht-standardisierte Handelspraktiken", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Teilnahme an Handelspraktiken, die von typischen Forex- oder Finanzmarkt-Handelspraktiken abweichen oder die dem Anbieter finanziellen oder anderen Schaden zufügen könnten.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Verwendung externer oder langsamer Datenfeeds", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Ausführung von Trades mit externen oder langsamen Datenfeeds.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Ausnutzen von Servicefehlern", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Verwendung von Handelsstrategien, die Fehler in unseren Dienstleistungen ausnutzen, wie z. B. Preisfehler oder verzögerte Aktualisierungen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Manipulatives Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Durchführung manipulativer Trades, wie z. B. das gleichzeitige Eingehen entgegengesetzter Positionen, entweder einzeln oder in Zusammenarbeit mit anderen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hedging über Konten", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hedging zwischen Konten mit anderen Bewertungsfirmen, die ähnlich wie Funded Trader Markets sind", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Kontoverwaltungsdienste", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Alle Konten in unseren Herausforderungen müssen nach Abschluss einer Phase ausschließlich vom Kontoinhaber gehandelt werden. Jede Abweichung von dieser Regel wird als Verstoß betrachtet.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Zusätzlich ist nur ein Händler pro Haushalt und IP-Adresse erlaubt. Ein Verstoß gegen diese Regel führt zur Kündigung aller beteiligten Konten.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Verbotene Handelspraktiken", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Gruppenhandel", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Gruppenhandel und das Kopieren von Trades von anderen sowie das Koordinieren und umgekehrte Handeln mit anderen sind nicht erlaubt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hochfrequenzhandel", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Der Handel mit großen Volumina von Positionen in sehr hoher Geschwindigkeit ist verboten.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Nachrichten-Skalping", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Das schnelle Öffnen und Schließen mehrerer Positionen innerhalb von Sekunden rund um wichtige Nachrichtenveröffentlichungen (z. B. FOMC, NFP, CPI), um von Marktbewegungen zu profitieren, ist nicht erlaubt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Arbitrage-Handel: Jegliche Form des Arbitrage-Handels, einschließlich Reverse- und Latency-Arbitrage, ist strengstens untersagt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Multi-Account Reverse Trading", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Reverse-Trading über mehrere Konten, insbesondere rund um Ereignisse wie FOMC, bei denen Sie Positionen über verschiedene Bewertungsfirmen absichern, ist nicht erlaubt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Tick Scalping", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Scalping in Ticks, das Öffnen und Schließen großer Positionsgrößen in Millisekunden umfasst, ist verboten, da es nicht live gespiegelt werden kann.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Interne Reverse-Handel", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Reverse-Handel innerhalb der internen Konten von Funded Trader Market ist nicht erlaubt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Trades kopieren", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Gruppenabsicherung", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Es ist strengstens untersagt, gegensätzliche Positionen über eine oder mehrere Bewertungsfirmen zu koordinieren, um Risiken zu manipulieren.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Kontoverwaltungsdienste", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Der Kauf oder die Bereitstellung von Kontomanagementdiensten oder die Nutzung von Dienstleistungen zur Weitergabe von Bewertungsfirmen ist nicht erlaubt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Kontenfreigabe", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Das Teilen von Kontoinformationen oder das Erlauben, dass jemand anderes in Ihrem Namen auf ein Konto zugreift, führt zur Kontoschließung.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Spiegeln von Trades", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Es ist nicht erlaubt, Trades von einem anderen Trader oder einer Gruppe von Tradern über mehrere Konten hinweg zu spiegeln.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hinweis", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn ein Händler bei einer der verbotenen Praktiken erwischt wird, behalten wir uns das Recht vor, das Konto zu schließen und alle damit verbundenen Auszahlungen ohne Rückerstattung einzubehalten.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'gibt-es-einschränkungen-bei-bestimmten-handelspraktiken-an-finanzierten-händler-märkten', 'Gibt es Einschränkungen bei bestimmten Handelspraktiken an den Märkten für finanzierte Händler?', 'Bei Funded Trader Markets ermöglichen wir es Händlern, ihre Handelsstile und -strategien ohne Einschränkungen zu wählen. Es ist jedoch entscheidend, unsere Richtlinien zu befolgen.', 761, 'de', 109),
('هل توجد أي قيود على بعض ممارسات التداول في أسواق المتداولين الممولين؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "في أسواق المتداولين الممولين، نمنح المتداولين القدرة على اختيار أنماط واستراتيجيات تداولهم دون قيود. ومع ذلك، من الضروري اتباع إرشاداتنا وتجنب الأنشطة التي تستغل أنظمتنا أو تنتهك ممارسات التداول العادلة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الأفعال التالية محظورة تمامًا:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "استخدام البرمجيات أو التقنيات التلاعبية", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": لا يُسمح باستخدام البرمجيات أو الذكاء الاصطناعي أو التقنيات فائقة السرعة أو طرق إدخال البيانات الجماعية التي تتلاعب أو تمنح ميزة غير عادلة في استخدام أنظمتنا.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "ممارسات التداول غير القياسية", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": الانخراط في ممارسات التداول التي تنحرف عن التداول النموذجي في سوق الفوركس أو الأسواق المالية، أو التي قد تسبب ضررًا ماليًا أو غيره للمزود.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "استخدام مصادر بيانات خارجية أو بطيئة", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": تنفيذ الصفقات باستخدام مصادر بيانات خارجية أو بطيئة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "استغلال أخطاء الخدمة", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "استخدام استراتيجيات التداول التي تستفيد من الأخطاء في خدماتنا، مثل أخطاء عرض الأسعار أو التحديثات المتأخرة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تداول تلاعب", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الانخراط في تداولات تلاعب، مثل الدخول في مراكز متعارضة متزامنة، سواء بشكل فردي أو بالتعاون مع الآخرين.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "التحوط عبر الحسابات", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "التحوط بين الحسابات مع شركات تقييم أخرى مشابهة لشركة Funded Trader Markets", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "خدمات إدارة الحسابات", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "يجب أن يتم تداول جميع الحسابات في تحدياتنا حصريًا من قبل مالك الحساب بمجرد الانتهاء من مرحلة. سيتم اعتبار أي انحراف عن هذه القاعدة انتهاكًا.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "بالإضافة إلى ذلك، يُسمح بتاجر واحد فقط لكل أسرة وعنوان IP. ستؤدي مخالفة هذه القاعدة إلى إنهاء جميع الحسابات المعنية.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "ممارسات التداول المحظورة", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "تداول المجموعات", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": لا يُسمح بتداول المجموعات ونسخ الصفقات من الآخرين، بالإضافة إلى التنسيق والتداول العكسي مع الآخرين.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "التداول عالي التردد", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": يُحظر الانخراط في التداول عالي التردد، والذي يتضمن تداول كميات كبيرة من المراكز بسرعات عالية جداً.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تداول الأخبار", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": يُمنع فتح وإغلاق عدة مراكز بسرعة خلال ثوانٍ حول إصدارات الأخبار ذات التأثير العالي (مثل FOMC، NFP، CPI) لاستغلال تدفقات السوق.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تداول التحكيم: أي شكل من أشكال تداول التحكيم، بما في ذلك التحكيم العكسي وتحكيم الكمون، محظور تمامًا.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تداول العكس عبر حسابات متعددة", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": تداول العكس عبر حسابات متعددة، خاصة حول أحداث مثل FOMC، حيث تقوم بتحوط المراكز عبر شركات تقييم مختلفة، غير مسموح به.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تداول النقاط", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": التداول السريع في النقاط، الذي يتضمن فتح وإغلاق أحجام كبيرة من المراكز في أجزاء من الثانية، محظور لأنه لا يمكن نسخه مباشرة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "التداول العكسي الداخلي", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": لا يُسمح بالتداول العكسي ضمن حسابات المتداولين الممولين في السوق.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "نسخ الصفقات", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "تغطية المجموعة", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": التنسيق بين المواقف المتعارضة عبر شركة تقييم واحدة أو أكثر للتلاعب بالمخاطر محظور تمامًا.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "خدمات إدارة الحسابات", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": شراء أو تقديم خدمات إدارة الحسابات أو استخدام خدمات تمرير شركة التقييم غير مسموح به.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "مشاركة الحساب", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "مشاركة معلومات الحساب أو السماح لشخص آخر بتمرير حساب نيابة عنك سيؤدي إلى إنهاء الحساب.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تداولات النسخ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "لا يُسمح بنسخ تداولات من متداول آخر أو مجموعة من المتداولين عبر حسابات متعددة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "ملاحظة", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ": إذا تم العثور على أي تاجر يشارك في أي من الممارسات المحظورة، فإننا نحتفظ بالحق في إغلاق الحساب وسحب أي مدفوعات مرتبطة دون استرداد.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'هل توجد أي قيود على بعض ممارسات التداول في أسواق المتداولين الممولين؟', 'هل توجد أي قيود على بعض ممارسات التداول في أسواق المتداولين الممولين؟', 'في Funded Trader Markets، نُمكّن المتداولين من اختيار أنماط واستراتيجيات التداول الخاصة بهم دون قيود. ومع ذلك، من الضروري اتباع إرشاداتنا...', 762, 'ar', 109),
('Adakah Terdapat Sebarang Had Terhadap Amalan Perdagangan Tertentu di Pasaran Pedagang Dibiayai?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Di Funded Trader Markets, kami memberdayakan peniaga untuk memilih gaya dan strategi perdagangan mereka tanpa sekatan. Walau bagaimanapun, adalah penting untuk mengikuti garis panduan kami dan mengelakkan aktiviti yang mengeksploitasi sistem kami atau melanggar amalan perdagangan yang adil.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Tindakan berikut adalah dilarang sama sekali:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Menggunakan Perisian atau Teknik Manipulatif", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Menggunakan perisian, AI, teknik ultra-pantas, atau kaedah kemasukan data besar yang memanipulasi atau memberikan kelebihan yang tidak adil dalam penggunaan sistem kami adalah tidak dibenarkan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Amalan Perdagangan Tidak Standard", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Terlibat dalam amalan perdagangan yang menyimpang dari perdagangan forex atau pasaran kewangan yang tipikal, atau yang boleh menyebabkan kerugian kewangan atau lain-lain kepada penyedia.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Menggunakan Aliran Data Luaran atau Perlahan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Melaksanakan perdagangan dengan aliran data luaran atau perlahan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Menyalahgunakan Ralat Perkhidmatan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Menggunakan strategi perdagangan yang memanfaatkan ralat dalam perkhidmatan kami, seperti ralat paparan harga atau kemas kini yang tertangguh.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Perdagangan Manipulatif", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Terlibat dalam perdagangan manipulatif, seperti memasuki posisi bertentangan secara serentak, sama ada secara individu atau dengan kerjasama orang lain.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Melindungi Antara Akaun", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Melindungi antara akaun dengan firma penilaian lain yang serupa dengan Funded Trader Markets", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Perkhidmatan Pengurusan Akaun", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Semua akaun dalam cabaran kami mesti diperdagangkan secara eksklusif oleh pemilik akaun setelah satu fasa selesai. Sebarang penyimpangan daripada peraturan ini akan dianggap sebagai pelanggaran.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Selain itu, hanya satu peniaga bagi setiap isi rumah dan alamat IP yang dibenarkan. Melanggar peraturan ini akan mengakibatkan penamatan semua akaun yang terlibat.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Amalan Perdagangan yang Dilarang", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Perdagangan Kumpulan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Perdagangan kumpulan dan menyalin perdagangan dari orang lain, serta menyelaraskan dan perdagangan terbalik dengan orang lain, adalah tidak dibenarkan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Perdagangan Frekuensi Tinggi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Mengambil bahagian dalam perdagangan frekuensi tinggi, yang melibatkan perdagangan jumlah posisi yang besar pada kelajuan yang sangat tinggi, adalah dilarang.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Skalping Berita", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Membuka dan menutup pelbagai posisi dengan cepat dalam beberapa saat sekitar pengumuman berita yang memberi impak tinggi (contohnya, FOMC, NFP, CPI) untuk mengeksploitasi maklumat pasaran adalah tidak dibenarkan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Perdagangan Arbitrage: Sebarang bentuk perdagangan arbitrage, termasuk arbitrage terbalik dan arbitrage latensi, adalah dilarang sama sekali.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Perdagangan Terbalik Multi-Akaun", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Perdagangan terbalik merentasi pelbagai akaun, terutamanya sekitar acara seperti FOMC, di mana anda melindungi kedudukan merentasi firma penilaian yang berbeza, adalah tidak dibenarkan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Scalping Tick", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Scalping dalam ticks, yang melibatkan pembukaan dan penutupan saiz posisi besar dalam milisaat, adalah dilarang kerana ia tidak dapat dicerminkan secara langsung.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Perdagangan Balik Dalaman", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Terlibat dalam perdagangan balik dalam akaun dalaman Pasaran Pedagang Dibiayai adalah tidak dibenarkan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Menyalin Perdagangan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengelompokan Lindung Nil