('How Does the 24-Hour Payout Guarantee Work?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The 24-hour payout guarantee ensures that you are eligible to receive your full payout within 24 business hours of your payout request.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If we fail to meet this time frame, we will double the requested payout and issue a free account of the same size.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "However, please be aware of the following conditions: Third-Party Payment Delays: Occasionally, there may be issues with third-party payment solutions.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If we reach out to you via email, Discord, or any other platform within the 24-hour period to request a change in payment method to process your payout on time, and you do not respond, this will void your eligibility for the double payout guarantee.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Maximum Payout Amount: This guarantee is only applicable for payouts up to $1000.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Business hours are defined as 8:00 AM EST to 5:00 PM EST, operating for 8 hours per day, Monday through Friday", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'how-does-the-24-hour-payout-guarantee-work', 'How Does the 24-Hour Payout Guarantee Work?', 'The 24-hour payout guarantee ensures that you are eligible to receive your full payout within 24 business hours of your payout request. If we fail to me...', 1368, 'en', 61),
('24 Saatlik Ödeme Garantisi Nasıl Çalışır?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "24 saat ödeme garantisi, ödeme talebinizin ardından 24 iş saati içinde tam ödemenizi alabilmeniz için uygun olduğunuzu garanti eder.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu zaman dilimine uymazsak, talep edilen ödemenizi iki katına çıkaracak ve aynı boyutta ücretsiz bir hesap vereceğiz.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ancak, lütfen aşağıdaki koşulları dikkate alın: Üçüncü Taraf Ödeme Gecikmeleri: Bazen üçüncü taraf ödeme çözümleriyle ilgili sorunlar olabilir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer 24 saatlik süre içinde size e-posta, Discord veya başka bir platform aracılığıyla ulaşarak ödemenizi zamanında işlemek için ödeme yönteminde bir değişiklik talep edersek ve siz yanıt vermezseniz, bu durum iki kat ödeme garantisi için uygunluğunuzu geçersiz kılacaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Maksimum Ödeme Tutarı: Bu garanti yalnızca $1000''a kadar olan ödemeler için geçerlidir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Çalışma saatleri, Pazartesi''den Cuma''ya kadar günde 8 saat, EST ile 8:00 AM''den 5:00 PM''e kadar tanımlanmaktadır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', '24 saat ödeme garantisi nasıl çalışır', '24 Saatlik Ödeme Garantisi Nasıl Çalışır?', '24 saat ödeme garantisi, ödeme talebinizin ardından 24 iş saati içinde tam ödemenizi alabilmeniz için uygun olduğunuzu garanti eder. Eğer bunu başaramazsak...', 1369, 'tr', 61),
('Wie funktioniert die 24-Stunden-Auszahlungsgarantie?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Die 24-Stunden-Auszahlungsgarantie stellt sicher, dass Sie berechtigt sind, Ihre volle Auszahlung innerhalb von 24 Geschäftsstunden nach Ihrer Auszahlungsanfrage zu erhalten.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn wir diesen Zeitrahmen nicht einhalten, verdoppeln wir die angeforderte Auszahlung und stellen ein kostenloses Konto in derselben Größe aus.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bitte beachten Sie jedoch die folgenden Bedingungen: Verzögerungen bei Drittanbieter-Zahlungen: Gelegentlich kann es Probleme mit Zahlungsdiensten von Drittanbietern geben.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn wir Sie innerhalb des 24-Stunden-Zeitraums per E-Mail, Discord oder einer anderen Plattform kontaktieren, um eine Änderung der Zahlungsmethode anzufordern, um Ihre Auszahlung rechtzeitig zu bearbeiten, und Sie nicht antworten, erlischt Ihre Berechtigung für die doppelte Auszahlungsgarantie.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Maximale Auszahlungsbetrag: Diese Garantie gilt nur für Auszahlungen bis zu 1000 $.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Die Geschäftszeiten sind definiert als 8:00 Uhr EST bis 17:00 Uhr EST, mit einer Betriebszeit von 8 Stunden pro Tag, von Montag bis Freitag.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'wie-funktioniert-die-24-stunden-auszahlungs-garantie', 'Wie funktioniert die 24-Stunden-Auszahlungsgarantie?', 'Die 24-Stunden-Auszahlungsgarantie stellt sicher, dass Sie berechtigt sind, Ihre vollständige Auszahlung innerhalb von 24 Geschäftsstunden nach Ihrer Auszahlungsanfrage zu erhalten. Wenn wir es versäumen, ...', 1370, 'de', 61),
('كيف تعمل ضمان الدفع خلال 24 ساعة؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "تضمن ضمان الدفع خلال 24 ساعة أنك مؤهل لاستلام المبلغ الكامل خلال 24 ساعة عمل من طلب الدفع الخاص بك.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا فشلنا في الوفاء بهذا الإطار الزمني، سنضاعف المبلغ المطلوب وسنصدر حسابًا مجانيًا بنفس الحجم.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "ومع ذلك، يرجى أن تكون على علم بالشروط التالية: تأخيرات الدفع من طرف ثالث: قد تحدث أحيانًا مشاكل مع حلول الدفع من طرف ثالث.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا تواصلنا معك عبر البريد الإلكتروني أو Discord أو أي منصة أخرى خلال فترة 24 ساعة لطلب تغيير طريقة الدفع لمعالجة دفعتك في الوقت المحدد، ولم ترد، فإن ذلك سيبطل أهليتك لضمان الدفع المزدوج.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "حد أقصى لمبلغ الدفع: هذا الضمان ينطبق فقط على المدفوعات التي تصل إلى 1000 دولار.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "ساعات العمل محددة من 8:00 صباحًا بتوقيت شرق الولايات المتحدة إلى 5:00 مساءً بتوقيت شرق الولايات المتحدة، وتعمل لمدة 8 ساعات يوميًا، من الاثنين إلى الجمعة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'كيف تعمل ضمان الدفع خلال 24 ساعة؟', 'كيف تعمل ضمان الدفع خلال 24 ساعة؟', 'تضمن ضمان الدفع خلال 24 ساعة أنك مؤهل لاستلام المبلغ الكامل خلال 24 ساعة عمل من طلب الدفع الخاص بك. إذا فشلنا في تلبية...', 1371, 'ar', 61),
('Bagaimana Jaminan Pembayaran 24 Jam Berfungsi?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jaminan pembayaran 24 jam memastikan bahawa anda layak untuk menerima pembayaran penuh anda dalam masa 24 jam perniagaan selepas permintaan pembayaran anda.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika kami gagal memenuhi tempoh masa ini, kami akan menggandakan jumlah pembayaran yang diminta dan mengeluarkan akaun percuma dengan saiz yang sama.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Walau bagaimanapun, sila ambil perhatian tentang syarat berikut: Kelewatan Pembayaran Pihak Ketiga: Kadang-kadang, mungkin terdapat masalah dengan penyelesaian pembayaran pihak ketiga.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika kami menghubungi anda melalui e-mel, Discord, atau mana-mana platform lain dalam tempoh 24 jam untuk meminta perubahan kaedah pembayaran bagi memproses pembayaran anda tepat pada masanya, dan anda tidak memberi maklum balas, ini akan membatalkan kelayakan anda untuk jaminan pembayaran berganda.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jumlah Pembayaran Maksimum: Jaminan ini hanya terpakai untuk pembayaran sehingga $1000.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Waktu perniagaan ditakrifkan sebagai 8:00 AM EST hingga 5:00 PM EST, beroperasi selama 8 jam sehari, dari Isnin hingga Jumaat.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'bagaimana-jaminan-pembayaran-24-jam-berfungsi', 'Bagaimana Jaminan Pembayaran 24 Jam Berfungsi?', 'Jaminan pembayaran 24 jam memastikan bahawa anda layak untuk menerima pembayaran penuh anda dalam masa 24 jam perniagaan selepas permintaan pembayaran anda. Jika kami gagal untuk memenuhi...', 1372, 'ms', 61),
('How Does the Maximum Daily Drawdown Limit for the 1-Step Nitro Pro Evaluation Work?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Maximum Daily Drawdown Limit is ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "2%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " of the Initial Balance.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "For a $100,000 1-Step Nitro Pro Evaluation, the Daily Drawdown is ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "2%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " of the Initial Balance.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Day 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Starting Balance/Equity: $100,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Allowed Daily Drawdown: 2% of $100,000 = $2,000 (stop-out limit = $98,000)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "ind