('Wie funktioniert das maximale tägliche Drawdown-Limit für die 1-Step Nitro Pro Bewertung?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Das maximale tägliche Rückgangslimit beträgt", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "2%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "des Anfangssaldos.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Für eine $100.000 1-Schritt Nitro Pro Bewertung beträgt der tägliche Drawdown", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "2%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "des Anfangssaldos.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tag 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Startguthaben/Eigenkapital: 100.000 $", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Erlaubter täglicher Rückgang: 2 % von $100.000 = $2.000 (Stop-Loss-Grenze = $98.000)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tag 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Endsaldo (Tag 1): $104.000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Ende des Tages Eigenkapital (Tag 1): $103.000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Um 17:00 Uhr EST, wenn unrealisierten Positionen offen sind, werden 2% des ursprünglichen Kontostands von dem höheren der beiden abgezogen. In Beispiel 2 oben, da der Kontostand höher als das Eigenkapital ist, wird die Stop-Out-Grenze ($104.000 – (2% von 100.000)) = $104.000 – $2.000 = $102.000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn entweder das Eigenkapital oder das Guthaben diese Grenze erreicht, würde dies zu einem Verstoß gegen die tägliche Drawdown-Grenze führen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'wie-funktioniert-das-maximale-tägliche-drawdown-limit-für-die-1-stufige-nitro-pro-bewertung', 'Wie funktioniert das maximale tägliche Drawdown-Limit für die 1-Step Nitro Pro Bewertung?', 'Das maximale tägliche Drawdown-Limit beträgt 2 % des Anfangsbalancs. Beispiel 1: Für eine 100.000 $ 1-Step Nitro Pro Bewertung beträgt der tägliche Drawdown 2 % des Ini...', 1384, 'de', 60),
