, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hari 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Baki Akhir Hari (Hari 1): $104,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Akhir Hari Ekuiti (Hari 1): $103,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pada pukul 5 PM EST, jika posisi yang belum direalisasikan terbuka, maka 2% daripada baki Awal akan ditolak dari yang lebih tinggi antara kedua-duanya. Dalam Contoh 2 di atas, kerana baki lebih tinggi daripada Ekuiti, had berhenti akan menjadi ($104,000 – (2% daripada 100,000)) = $104,000 – $2,000 = $102,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika sama ada Ekuiti atau Baki mencapai had ini, ia akan mengakibatkan pelanggaran Had Penarikan Harian.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'bagaimana-had-penarikan-harian-maksimum-untuk-evaluasi-1-langkah-nitro-pro-berfungsi', 'Bagaimana Had Penarikan Harian Maksimum untuk Penilaian 1-Step Nitro Pro Berfungsi?', 'Had Harian Penarikan Maksimum adalah 2% daripada Baki Awal. Contoh 1: Untuk Penilaian Nitro Pro 1 Langkah bernilai $100,000, Penarikan Harian adalah 2% daripada In...', 1386, 'ms', 60),
('How Does the Overall Drawdown Limit for the 1-Step Nitro Pro Evaluation Work?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Overall Drawdown Limit for the 1-Step Nitro Evaluation is 3", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ".", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Key Points to Understand:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "– ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Trailing Overall Drawdown:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " The Overall Drawdown is calculated based on your account’s Highest Balance (Maximum Balance Watermark) and does not reset daily at 5 PM EST. It consistently remains at 3% of the peak balance.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "– ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Fixed Drawdown After Profit", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Once the account achieves a 3% profit, the Overall Drawdown Limit is fixed based on the Initial Account size, and the highest recorded balance no longer affects the limit.", "type": "t