('Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Mengenai Konsistensi pada Program Nitro Pro?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun Nitro Pro 1-langkah, terdapat peraturan konsistensi yang terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Dana Simulasi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Mengapa Peraturan ini?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Konsistensi Pasaran Pedagang Berpendanaan mempromosikan pertumbuhan keuntungan yang stabil dan membantu pedagang mengelakkan perdagangan yang beremosi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Butiran Penting Mengenai Peraturan Konsistensi Untuk Akaun Nitro Pro 1-langkah", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Cabaran; anda tidak seharusnya membuat lebih daripada 20% daripada sasaran keuntungan dalam satu hari.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Simulasi Dibiayai; anda tidak seharusnya membuat lebih daripada 20% daripada jumlah keuntungan dalam satu hari.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika keuntungan dalam satu hari melebihi 20% daripada sasaran keuntungan anda dalam Fasa Cabaran atau lebih daripada 20% daripada jumlah keuntungan anda dalam Fasa Simulasi Dibiayai, anda perlu terus berdagang sehingga tidak ada hari dengan lebih daripada maksimum yang dinyatakan di atas.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bilakah Peraturan Konsistensi Diperlukan?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk Akaun Nitro Pro 1-langkah, ia terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengiraan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "[Hari Terbaik % daripada Jumlah Keuntungan] = [Keuntungan Hari Terbaik] ÷ [Jumlah Keuntungan] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Keuntungan Hari Terbaik