Nitro Pro 1-langkah – Fasa Cabaran)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk Akaun Nitro Pro bernilai $10,000 dengan sasaran keuntungan Fasa 1 sebanyak $1,000 (10%), keuntungan pada mana-mana hari tidak boleh melebihi $200 (20% daripada sasaran) untuk kekal dalam peraturan konsistensi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dengan mematuhi garis panduan ini, pedagang dapat memupuk pendekatan perdagangan yang berdisiplin dan mampan, yang penting untuk kejayaan jangka panjang.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'adakah peraturan mengenai konsistensi pada program nitro pro', 'Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Mengenai Konsistensi pada Program Nitro Pro?', 'Untuk akaun Nitro Pro 1-langkah, terdapat peraturan konsistensi yang terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi. Mengapa Peraturan ini? Perdagangan yang Dibiayai...', 1498, 'ms', 52),
('Is There A Rule Regarding Consistency for 1-Step Nitro Accounts?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "For 1-step Nitro accounts, there’s a consistency rule that applies to both the Challenge Phase and Simulated Funded Phase", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Why this Rule?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Funded Trader Markets’ Consistency Rule promotes steady profit growth and helps traders avoid emotional trading.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Important Details About the Consistency Rule For Evaluation Accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In the Challenge Phase; you should not make more than 50% (i.e. half) of the profit target in one day.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In the Simulated Funded Phase; you should not have made more than 45% of the total profit in one day.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If a single day’s profit is more than 50% of your profit target in the Challenge Phase or more than 45% of your total profit in the Simulated Funded Phase, you have to continue trading until there isn’t a day with more than the above said maximums.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "When is the Consistency Rule Required?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "For evaluation accounts, it applies to both the Challenge Phase and Simulated Funded Phase", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Calculation", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "[Best Day % of Total Profit] = [Best Day Profit] ÷ [Overall Profit] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Best Day Profit means the highest single day profit", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Single Day’s Profit = Balance at 5pm EST Today – Balance at 5pm EST Yesterday", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example (Simulated Funded Phase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If you made a total profit of $5,000 in the Simulated Funded Phase,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "To be eligible for withdrawal, there should not have been a single day with more than 45% of $5,000 (= $2,250).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If there is a single day with more than 45% of total profit, then you have to keep on trading until the best day profit is less than 45% of the total profit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example (Challenge Phase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "For a $10,000 1-step Nitro account with a Phase 1 profit target of $1000 (10%), no single day’s profit should exceed $500 (50% of the target) to stay within the consistency rule.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If you achieve a $1000 total profit but make more than $500 in a single day, you are required to continue trading until the best day profit is less than 50% of the total profit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Success requires devising a strategy that prevents exceeding a $500 daily profit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "By adhering to these guidelines, traders can foster a disciplined and sustainable trading approach, crucial for long-term success.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'is-there-a-rule-regarding-consistency-for-1-step-nitro-accounts', 'Is There A Rule Regarding Consistency for 1-Step Nitro Accounts?', 'For 1-step Nitro accounts, there’s a consistency rule that applies to both the Challenge Phase and Simulated Funded Phase Why this Rule? Funded Trader M...', 1508, 'en', 51),
('1 Adım Nitro Hesapları için Tutarlılık ile İlgili Bir Kural Var mı?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "1 adım Nitro hesapları için, Hem Challenge Aşaması hem de Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşaması için geçerli olan bir tutarlılık kuralı vardır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu Kural neden?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Fonlu Trader Pazarları''nın Tutarlılık Kuralı, sürekli kar büyümesini teşvik eder ve traderların duygusal ticaretten kaçınmalarına yardımcı olur.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Değerlendirme Hesapları İçin Tutarlılık Kuralı Hakkında Önemli Detaylar", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Challenge Aşamasında; bir günde kâr hedefinin %50''sinden (yani yarısından) fazlasını yapmamalısınız.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşamasında; bir günde toplam kârın %45''inden fazlasını yapmamış olmalısınız.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer bir günde elde edilen kâr, Challenge Aşamasındaki kâr hedefinizin %50''sinden veya Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşamasındaki toplam kârınızın %45''inden fazlaysa, yukarıda belirtilen maksimumların üzerinde bir gün olmadığı sürece işlem yapmaya devam etmelisiniz.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tutarlılık Kuralı ne zaman gereklidir?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Değerlendirme hesapları için, bu hem Challenge Phase hem de Simulated Funded Phase için geçerlidir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hesaplama", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "[En İyi Gün % Toplam Kâr] = [En İyi Gün Kârı] ÷ [Toplam Kâr] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Best Day Profit, en yüksek tek günlük kârı ifade eder.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tek Günlük Kar = Bugün EST 17:00''deki Bakiyeniz – Dün EST 17:00''deki Bakiyeniz", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek (Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşaması)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşaması''nda toplamda $5,000 kar ettiyseniz,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Para çekme işlemi için, $5,000''ın (%45 = $2,250) üzerinde bir gün olmamalıdır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer toplam kârın %45''inden fazla olan tek bir gün varsa, en iyi gün kârı toplam kârın %45''inden az olana kadar işlem yapmaya devam etmelisiniz.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek (Meydan Okuma Aşaması)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "10.000 $ değerinde 1 adım Nitro hesabı için 1. Aşama kâr hedefi 1000 $ (yüzde 10) olduğunda, tutarlılık kuralına uymak için tek bir günün kârı 500 $''ı (hedefin %50''si) geçmemelidir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "1000 $ toplam kâr elde ederseniz ancak tek bir günde 500 $''dan fazla kazanırsanız, toplam kârın %50''sinden az olana kadar işlem yapmaya devam etmeniz gerekmektedir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Başarı, günlük 500 $''lık karı aşmayı önleyen bir strateji geliştirmeyi gerektirir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu yönergelere uyarak, yatırımcılar disiplinli ve sürdürülebilir bir ticaret yaklaşımını teşvik edebilir, bu da uzun vadeli başarı için kritik öneme sahiptir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', '1 adım nitro hesapları için tutarlılık ile ilgili bir kural var mı?', '1 Adım Nitro Hesapları için Tutarlılık ile İlgili Bir Kural Var mı?', '1 adım Nitro hesapları için, Hem Challenge Aşaması hem de Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşaması için geçerli olan bir tutarlılık kuralı vardır. Bu Kural Neden? Fonlanan Tüccar M...', 1509, 'tr', 51),
('Gibt es eine Regel zur Konsistenz für 1-Schritt Nitro-Konten?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Für 1-Schritt Nitro-Konten gilt eine Konsistenzregel, die sowohl für die Challenge-Phase als auch für die simulierte finanzierte Phase Anwendung findet.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Warum diese Regel?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Die Konsistenzregel der finanzierten Trader-Märkte fördert ein stetiges Gewinnwachstum und hilft Tradern, emotionales Trading zu vermeiden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wichtige Details zur Konsistenzregel für Evaluierungskonten", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In der Challenge-Phase sollten Sie an einem Tag nicht mehr als 50 % (d.h. die Hälfte) des Gewinnziels erreichen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In der simulierten finanzierten Phase sollten Sie an einem Tag nicht mehr als 45 % des Gesamtgewinns erzielt haben.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn der Gewinn eines einzelnen Tages mehr als 50 % Ihres Gewinnziels in der Challenge-Phase oder mehr als 45 % Ihres Gesamtgewinns in der simulierten finanzierten Phase beträgt, müssen Sie weiterhin handeln, bis es keinen Tag mit mehr als den oben genannten Höchstwerten gibt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wann ist die Konsistenzregel erforderlich?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Für Evaluierungsaccounts gilt dies sowohl für die Challenge-Phase als auch für die simulierte finanzierte Phase.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Berechnung", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "[Bester Tag % des Gesamtnutzens] = [Bester Tag Gewinn] ÷ [Gesamtgewinn] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Best Day Profit bedeutet den höchsten Gewinn an einem einzelnen Tag.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Gewinn eines einzelnen Tages = Kontostand um 17 Uhr EST heute – Kontostand um 17 Uhr EST gestern", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel (Simulierte Finanzierungsphase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Sie in der simulierten Finanzierungsphase einen Gesamtnutzen von 5.000 $ erzielt haben,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Um für eine Auszahlung berechtigt zu sein, darf es keinen einzigen Tag gegeben haben, an dem mehr als 45 % von 5.000 $ (= 2.250 $) überschritten wurden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn es einen einzigen Tag mit mehr als 45 % des Gesamtgewinns gibt, müssen Sie weiterhin handeln, bis der Gewinn des besten Tages weniger als 45 % des Gesamtgewinns beträgt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel (Herausforderungsphase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Für ein 10.000 $ 1-Schritt Nitro-Konto mit einem Gewinnziel der Phase 1 von 1.000 $ (10 %) sollte der Gewinn an keinem einzelnen Tag 500 $ (50 % des Ziels) überschreiten, um innerhalb der Konsistenzregel zu bleiben.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Sie einen Gesamtgewinn von 1.000 $ erzielen, aber an einem einzigen Tag mehr als 500 $ verdienen, sind Sie verpflichtet, weiterhin zu handeln, bis der Gewinn des besten Tages weniger als 50 % des Gesamtgewinns beträgt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Erfolg erfordert die Entwicklung einer Strategie, die verhindert, dass ein täglicher Gewinn von 500 $ überschritten wird.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Durch die Einhaltung dieser Richtlinien können Händler einen disziplinierten und nachhaltigen Handelsansatz fördern, der für den langfristigen Erfolg entscheidend ist.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'gibt-es-eine-regel-fuer-die-konsistenz-von-1-schritt-nitro-konten', 'Gibt es eine Regel zur Konsistenz für 1-Schritt Nitro-Konten?', 'Für 1-Schritt-Nitro-Konten gilt eine Konsistenzregel, die sowohl für die Challenge-Phase als auch 