('هل هناك قاعدة تتعلق بالاتساق لحسابات النيترو ذات الخطوة الواحدة؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "بالنسبة لحسابات Nitro ذات الخطوة الواحدة، هناك قاعدة اتساق تنطبق على كل من مرحلة التحدي ومرحلة التمويل المحاكية", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "لماذا هذا القانون؟", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "تروج قاعدة الاتساق في أسواق المتداولين الممولين لنمو الأرباح المستمر وتساعد المتداولين على تجنب التداول العاطفي.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "تفاصيل مهمة حول قاعدة الاتساق لحسابات التقييم", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "في مرحلة التحدي؛ يجب ألا تحقق أكثر من 50% (أي نصف) من هدف الربح في يوم واحد.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "في مرحلة التمويل المحاكية؛ يجب ألا تحقق أكثر من 45% من إجمالي الربح في يوم واحد.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا كان ربح يوم واحد أكثر من 50% من هدف ربحك في مرحلة التحدي أو أكثر من 45% من إجمالي ربحك في مرحلة التمويل المحاكية، يجب عليك الاستمرار في التداول حتى لا يكون هناك يوم يتجاوز الحدود القصوى المذكورة أعلاه.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "متى تكون قاعدة الاتساق مطلوبة؟", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "بالنسبة لحسابات التقييم، ينطبق ذلك على كل من مرحلة التحدي ومرحلة التمويل المحاكية", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "حساب", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "[أفضل يوم % من إجمالي الربح] = [أفضل يوم ربح] ÷ [إجمالي الربح] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "يعني أفضل ربح يومي أعلى ربح ليوم واحد", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "ربح يوم واحد = الرصيد عند الساعة 5 مساءً بتوقيت شرق الولايات المتحدة اليوم - الرصيد عند الساعة 5 مساءً بتوقيت شرق الولايات المتحدة أمس", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال (مرحلة التمويل المحاكية)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا حققت ربحًا إجماليًا قدره 5000 دولار في مرحلة التمويل المحاكية،", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "لكي تكون مؤهلاً للسحب، يجب ألا يكون هناك يوم واحد تجاوز فيه الربح 45% من 5000 دولار (= 2250 دولار).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا كان هناك يوم واحد يحقق أكثر من 45% من إجمالي الربح، فعليك الاستمرار في التداول حتى يكون أفضل ربح يومي أقل من 45% من إجمالي الربح.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال (مرحلة التحدي)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "بالنسبة لحساب نيترو من خطوة واحدة بقيمة 10,000 دولار مع هدف ربح في المرحلة 1 قدره 1,000 دولار (10%)، يجب ألا يتجاوز ربح أي يوم واحد 500 دولار (50% من الهدف) للبقاء ضمن قاعدة الاتساق.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا حققت ربحًا إجماليًا قدره 1,000 دولار ولكنك حققت أكثر من 500 دولار في يوم واحد، يتعين عليك الاستمرار في التداول حتى يكون أفضل ربح يومي أقل من 50% من إجمالي الربح.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "يتطلب النجاح وضع استراتيجية تمنع تجاوز ربح يومي قدره 500 دولار.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "من خلال الالتزام بهذه الإرشادات، يمكن للمتداولين تعزيز نهج تداول منضبط ومستدام، وهو أمر حاسم للنجاح على المدى الطويل.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'هل هناك قاعدة تتعلق بالاتساق لحسابات النيترو ذات الخطوة الواحدة؟', 'هل هناك قاعدة تتعلق بالاتساق لحسابات النيترو ذات الخطوة الواحدة؟', 'بالنسبة لحسابات Nitro ذات الخطوة الواحدة، هناك قاعدة اتساق تنطبق على كل من مرحلة التحدي ومرحلة التمويل المحاكية. لماذا هذه القاعدة؟ المتداول الممول م...', 1511, 'ar', 51),
('Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Mengenai Konsistensi untuk Akaun Nitro 1-Langkah?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun Nitro 1-langkah, terdapat peraturan konsistensi yang terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Mengapa Peraturan ini?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Konsistensi Pasaran Pedagang Berpendanaan mempromosikan pertumbuhan keuntungan yang stabil dan membantu pedagang mengelakkan perdagangan yang beremosi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Butiran Penting Mengenai Peraturan Konsistensi Untuk Akaun Penilaian", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Cabaran; anda tidak seharusnya membuat lebih daripada 50% (iaitu separuh) daripada sasaran keuntungan dalam satu hari.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Simulasi Dibiayai; anda tidak seharusnya telah membuat lebih daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan dalam satu hari.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika keuntungan dalam satu hari melebihi 50% daripada sasaran keuntungan anda dalam Fasa Cabaran atau lebih daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan anda dalam Fasa Simulasi Dibiayai, anda perlu terus berdagang sehingga tiada hari yang melebihi maksimum yang dinyatakan di atas.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bilakah Peraturan Konsistensi Diperlukan?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun penilaian, ia terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengiraan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "[Hari Terbaik % daripada Jumlah Keuntungan] = [Keuntungan Hari Terbaik] ÷ [Jumlah Keuntungan] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Keuntungan Hari Terbaik bermaksud keuntungan hari tunggal tertinggi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Keuntungan Hari Tunggal = Baki pada 5pm EST Hari Ini – Baki pada 5pm EST Semalam", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh (Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda memperoleh keuntungan keseluruhan sebanyak $5,000 dalam Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk layak mengeluarkan wang, tidak boleh ada satu hari pun dengan lebih daripada 45% daripada $5,000 (= $2,250).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika terdapat satu hari dengan lebih daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan, maka anda perlu terus berdagang sehingga keuntungan hari terbaik kurang daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh (Fasa Cabaran)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun Nitro 1-langkah bernilai $10,000 dengan sasaran keuntungan Fasa 1 sebanyak $1000 (10%), keuntungan pada mana-mana hari tidak boleh melebihi $500 (50% daripada sasaran) untuk kekal dalam peraturan konsistensi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda mencapai keuntungan keseluruhan $1000 tetapi memperoleh lebih daripada $500 dalam satu hari, anda dikehendaki untuk terus berdagang sehingga keuntungan hari terbaik kurang daripada 50% daripada jumlah keuntungan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Kejayaan memerlukan merangka strategi yang menghalang melebihi keuntungan harian sebanyak $500.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dengan mematuhi garis panduan ini, pedagang dapat memupuk pendekatan perdagangan yang berdisiplin dan mampan, yang penting untuk kejayaan jangka panjang.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'adakah-peraturan-mengenai-konsistensi-untuk-akaun-nitro-1-langkah', 'Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Mengenai Konsistensi untuk Akaun Nitro 1-Langkah?', 'Untuk akaun Nitro 1-langkah, terdapat peraturan konsistensi yang terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi. Mengapa Peraturan Ini? Pedagang yang Dibiayai M...', 1512, 'ms', 51),
('Is There A Rule Regarding Consistency for 2-Step Standard Accounts?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "For 2-step Standard accounts, there’s a consistency rule that applies to both the Challenge Phase and Simulated Funded Phase", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Why this Rule?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Funded Trader Markets’ Consistency Rule promotes steady profit growth and helps traders avoid emotional trading.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Important Details About the Consistency Rule For Evaluation Accounts", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In the Challenge Phase; you should not make more than 50% (i.e. half) of the profit target in one day.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In the Simulated Funded Phase; you should not have made more than 45% of the total profit in one day.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If a single day’s profit is more than 50% of your profit target in the Challenge Phase or more than 45% of your total profit in the Simulated Funded Phase, you have to continue trading until there isn’t a day with more than the above said maximums.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "When is the Consistency Rule Required?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "For evaluation accounts, it applies to both the Challenge Phase and Simulated Funded Phase", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Calculation", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "[Best Day % of Total Profit] = [Best Day Profit] ÷ [Overall Profit] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Best Day Profit means the highest single day profit", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Single Day’s Profit = Balance at 5pm EST Today – Balance at 5pm EST Yesterday", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example (Simulated Funded Phase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 3, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If you made a total profit of $5,000 in the Simulated Funded Phase,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "To be eligible for withdrawal, there should not have been a single day with more than 45% of $5,000 (= $2,250).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If there is a single day with more than 45% of total profit, then you have to keep on trading until the best day profit is less than 45% of the total profit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example (Challenge Phase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "For a $25,000 account with a Phase 2 profit target of $1250 (5%), no single day’s profit should exceed $625 (50% of the target) to stay within the consistency rule.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If you achieve a $1250 total profit but make more than $625 in a single day, you are required to continue trading until the best day profit is less than 50% of the total profit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Success requires devising a strategy that prevents exceeding a $625 daily profit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "By adhering to these guidelines, traders can foster a disciplined and sustainable trading approach, crucial for long-term success.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'is-there-a-rule-regarding-consistency-for-2-step-standard-accounts', 'Is There A Rule Regarding Consistency for 2-Step Standard Accounts?', 'For 2-step Standard accounts, there’s a consistency rule that applies to both the Challenge Phase and Simulated Funded Phase Why this Rule? Funded Trade...', 1522, 'en', 50),
('2 Aşamalı Standart Hesaplar için Tutarlılık ile İlgili Bir Kural Var mı?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "2 adımlı Standart hesaplar için, Hem Zorluk Aşaması hem de Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşaması için geçerli olan bir tutarlılık kuralı vardır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu Kural neden?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Fonlu Trader Pazarları''nın Tutarlılık Kuralı, sürekli kar büyümesini teşvik eder ve traderların duygusal ticaretten kaçınmalarına yardımcı olur.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Değerlendirme Hesapları İçin Tutarlılık Kuralı Hakkında Önemli Detaylar", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Challenge Aşamasında; bir günde kâr hedefinin %50''sinden (yani yarısından) fazlasını yapmamalısınız.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşamasında; bir günde toplam kârın %45''inden fazlasını yapmamış olmalısınız.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer bir günde elde edilen kâr, Challenge Aşamasındaki kâr hedefinizin %50''sinden veya Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşamasındaki toplam kârınızın %45''inden fazlaysa, yukarıda belirtilen maksimumların üzerinde bir gün olmadığı sürece işlem yapmaya devam etmelisiniz.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tutarlılık Kuralı ne zaman gereklidir?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Değerlendirme hesapları için, bu hem Challenge Phase hem de Simulated Funded Phase için geçerlidir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hesaplama", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "[En İyi Gün % Toplam Kâr] = [En İyi Gün Kârı] ÷ [Toplam Kâr] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Best Day Profit, en yüksek tek günlük kârı ifade eder.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tek Günlük Kar = Bugün EST 17:00''deki Bakiyeniz – Dün EST 17:00''deki Bakiyeniz", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek (Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşaması)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 3, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Simüle Edilmiş Fonlama Aşaması''nda toplamda $5,000 kar ettiyseniz,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Para çekme işlemi için, $5,000''ın (%45 = $2,250) üzerinde bir gün olmamalıdır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer toplam kârın %45''inden fazla olan tek bir gün varsa, en iyi gün kârı toplam kârın %45''inden az olana kadar işlem yapmaya devam etmelisiniz.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek (Meydan Okuma Aşaması)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "$25,000''lık bir hesap için, $1250 (5%)''lik bir Aşama 2 kâr hedefinde, tek bir günün kârı $625''i (hedefin %50''si) aşmamalıdır, böylece tutarlılık kuralına uyulmuş olur.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "$1250 toplam kâr elde ederseniz ancak tek bir günde $625''ten fazla kazanırsanız, toplam kârın %50''sinden az olduğu en iyi gün kârına ulaşana kadar işlem yapmaya devam etmeniz gerekmektedir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Başarı, günlük 625 $''lık kârı aşmayı önleyen bir strateji geliştirmeyi gerektirir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu yönergelere uyarak, yatırımcılar disiplinli ve sürdürülebilir bir ticaret yaklaşımını teşvik edebilir, bu da uzun vadeli başarı için kritik öneme sahiptir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', '2 adımlı standart hesaplar için tutarlılık ile ilgili bir kural var mı?', '2 Aşamalı Standart Hesaplar için Tutarlılık ile İlgili Bir Kural Var mı?', '2 adımda Standart hesaplar için, Hem Challenge Aşaması hem de Simüle Edilmiş Fonlu Aşama için geçerli bir tutarlılık kuralı vardır. Bu Kural Neden Var? Fonlu Ticaret...', 1523, 'tr', 50),
('Gibt es eine Regel zur Konsistenz für 2-Schritt-Standardkonten?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Für Standardkonten mit 2-Schritt-Verfahren gilt eine Konsistenzregel, die sowohl für die Challenge-Phase als auch für die simulierte finanzierte Phase Anwendung findet.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Warum diese Regel?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Die Konsistenzregel der finanzierten Trader-Märkte fördert ein stetiges Gewinnwachstum und hilft Tradern, emotionales Trading zu vermeiden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wichtige Details zur Konsistenzregel für Evaluierungskonten", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In der Challenge-Phase sollten Sie an einem Tag nicht mehr als 50 % (d.h. die Hälfte) des Gewinnziels erreichen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In der simulierten finanzierten Phase sollten Sie an einem Tag nicht mehr als 45 % des Gesamtgewinns erzielt haben.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn der Gewinn eines einzelnen Tages mehr als 50 % Ihres Gewinnziels in der Challenge-Phase oder mehr als 45 % Ihres Gesamtgewinns in der simulierten finanzierten Phase beträgt, müssen Sie weiterhin handeln, bis es keinen Tag mit mehr als den oben genannten Höchstwerten gibt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wann ist die Konsistenzregel erforderlich?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Für Evaluierungsaccounts gilt dies sowohl für die Challenge-Phase als auch für die simulierte finanzierte Phase.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Berechnung", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "[Bester Tag % des Gesamtnutzens] = [Bester Tag Gewinn] ÷ [Gesamtgewinn] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Best Day Profit bedeutet den höchsten Gewinn an einem einzelnen Tag.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Gewinn eines einzelnen Tages = Kontostand um 17 Uhr EST heute – Kontostand um 17 Uhr EST gestern", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel (Simulierte Finanzierungsphase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 3, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Sie in der simulierten Finanzierungsphase einen Gesamtnutzen von 5.000 $ erzielt haben,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Um für eine Auszahlung berechtigt zu sein, darf es keinen einzigen Tag gegeben haben, an dem mehr als 45 % von 5.000 $ (= 2.250 $) überschritten wurden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn es einen einzigen Tag mit mehr als 45 % des Gesamtgewinns gibt, müssen Sie weiterhin handeln, bis der Gewinn des besten Tages weniger als 45 % des Gesamtgewinns beträgt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel (Herausforderungsphase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Für ein Konto von 25.000 $ mit einem Gewinnziel der Phase 2 von 1.250 $ (5 %) sollte der Gewinn an einem einzelnen Tag 625 $ (50 % des Ziels) nicht überschreiten, um innerhalb der Konsistenzregel zu bleiben.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Sie einen Gesamtnutzen von 1.250 $ erzielen, aber an einem einzelnen Tag mehr als 625 $ verdienen, sind Sie verpflichtet, weiter zu handeln, bis der beste Tagesgewinn weniger als 50 % des Gesamtnutzens beträgt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Erfolg erfordert die Entwicklung einer Strategie, die verhindert, dass ein täglicher Gewinn von 625 $ überschritten wird.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Durch die Einhaltung dieser Richtlinien können Händler einen disziplinierten und nachhaltigen Handelsansatz fördern, der für den langfristigen Erfolg entscheidend ist.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'gibt-es-eine-regel-zur-konsistenz-fuer-2-stufige-standardkonten', 'Gibt es eine Regel zur Konsistenz für 2-Schritt-Standardkonten?', 'Für Standardkonten mit 2-Schritt-Verfahren gilt eine Konsistenzregel, die sowohl für die Challen