('Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Mengenai Konsistensi untuk Akaun Kelajuan 2-Langkah?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun Kelajuan 2-langkah, terdapat peraturan konsistensi yang terpakai untuk kedua-dua Fasa Cabaran dan Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Mengapa Peraturan ini?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Konsistensi Pasaran Pedagang Berpendanaan mempromosikan pertumbuhan keuntungan yang stabil dan membantu pedagang mengelakkan perdagangan yang beremosi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Butiran Penting Mengenai Peraturan Konsistensi Untuk Akaun Penilaian", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Cabaran; anda tidak seharusnya membuat lebih daripada 50% (iaitu separuh) daripada sasaran keuntungan dalam satu hari.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Simulasi Dibiayai; anda tidak seharusnya telah 