aik bermaksud keuntungan hari tunggal tertinggi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Keuntungan Hari Tunggal = Baki pada 5pm EST Hari Ini – Baki pada 5pm EST Semalam", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh (Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda memperoleh keuntungan keseluruhan sebanyak $5,000 dalam Fasa Pembiayaan Simulasi,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk layak mengeluarkan wang, tidak boleh ada satu hari pun dengan lebih daripada 45% daripada $5,000 (= $2,250).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika terdapat satu hari dengan lebih daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan, maka anda perlu terus berdagang sehingga keuntungan hari terbaik kurang daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh (Fasa Cabaran)", "type": "text", "style": "", 