('Why is the country of the IP important during purchase and KYC?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"tag": "ol", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "We require the country of the IP address used during purchase to match the country from which the KYC verification is completed. This ensures compliance with our policies and enhances security.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Purchases or KYC submissions made through a VPN and/or VPS are strictly prohibited.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Trading with a VPN on the trading platform itself is allowed provided the IP connected to the VPN isn’t originating from any of our restricted countries. However, accessing our dashboard with a VPN/VPS isn’t allowed.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 4, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "United States IP is only allowed to use MatchTrader and TradeLocker. US is not allowed on MT5 and CTrader", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "number", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If any of the above policies are violated, Funded Trader Markets reserves the right to terminate the account or user without a refund.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Note:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "In the case where you are travelling, we recommend completing the purchase and KYC process while in your registered country of residence to avoid discrepancies. If travel is necessary, please contact our support team for guidance before proceeding.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'why-is-the-country-of-the-ip-important-during-purchase-and-kyc', 'Why is the country of the IP important during purchase and KYC?', 'We require the country of the IP address used during purchase to match the country from which the KYC verification is completed. This ensures compliance...', 1592, 'en', 45),
('IP''nin bulunduğu ülke, satın alma ve KYC sırasında neden önemlidir?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"tag": "ol", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Satın alma sırasında kullanılan IP adresinin ülkesinin, KYC doğrulamasının tamamlandığı ülkeyle eşleşmesini talep ediyoruz. Bu, politikalarımıza uyumu sağlar ve güvenliği artırır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "VPN ve/veya VPS aracılığıyla yapılan satın almalar veya KYC başvuruları kesinlikle yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ticaret platformunda VPN ile ticaret yapmak, VPN''e bağlı IP''nin kısıtlı ülkelerden birinden gelmediği sürece izinlidir. Ancak, bir VPN/VPS ile kontrol panelimize erişim sağlamak yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 4, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Amerika Birleşik Devletleri IP''si yalnızca MatchTrader ve TradeLocker kullanmak için izinlidir. ABD, MT5 ve CTrader''da kullanıma kapalıdır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "number", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Yukarıdaki politikaların herhangi birinin ihlal edilmesi durumunda, Funded Trader Markets hesabı veya kullanıcıyı geri ödeme yapmadan sonlandırma hakkını saklı tutar.