('Adakah Terdapat Had Pembayaran pada Pelan 1 Step Nitro X dan Bagaimana Ia Mempengaruhi Had Kerugian Maksimum Saya?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ya, Simulated Funded Nitro X mempunyai had pembayaran sebanyak $5,000 bagi setiap akaun untuk setiap permintaan pembayaran. Anda boleh meminta 50% daripada keuntungan anda, sehingga had $5,000, setelah anda memenuhi kriteria perdagangan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Keuntungan yang tinggal (50% yang lain, atau apa yang tinggal selepas had) menjadi Had Kerugian Maksimum anda, memastikan akaun anda tidak jatuh di bawah ambang ini untuk mengelakkan pelanggaran.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Akaun $50,000: Anda memperoleh $12,000 dalam keuntungan dan memenuhi semua kriteria. Anda boleh mengeluarkan 50% ($6,000), tetapi had mengehadkan anda kepada $5,000, meninggalkan $7,000 sebagai Had Kerugian Maksimum anda. Akaun anda tidak boleh jatuh di bawah $7,000 dalam penarikan, atau ia akan melanggar.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 