('Martingale/katmanlama izinli mi?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Evet, martingale ve katmanlama stratejileri tek bir hesap içinde izinlidir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Ancak, bu stratejiler birden fazla hesapta kullanılmamalıdır; bu, manipülasyon veya strateji istismarı önlemek içindir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Aynı çifti birden fazla hesapta açmak yalnızca aşağıdaki koşullar altında izin verilmektedir:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hesap A''da XAUUSD üzerinde bir Alım pozisyonu açabilir ve Hesap B''de XAUUSD üzerinde başka bir Alım pozisyonu açabilirsiniz, her iki pozisyon da", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "birbirini takip eden 5 dakika içinde açıldığı sürece.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ".", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer pozisyonlar birbirini takip eden 5 dakika içinde açılmazsa, Hesap B''deki pozisyon yalnızca Hesap A''daki pozisyon açıldıktan sonra açılabilir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "tamamen kapalı", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ".", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "madde", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Önemli:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Aynı paritedeki pozisyonlar farklı hesaplar arasında 5 dakikadan fazla bir süreyle açılırsa, bu tür bir faaliyetle elde edilen herhangi bir kar", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "tüm ilgili hesaplarda", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "ödeme için uygun olmayacaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu davranış, hesaplar arasında ardışık ticaret olarak sınıflandırılır ve kesinlikle yasaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "madde", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'martingale katmanına izin veriliyor mu', 'Martingale/katmanlama izinli mi?', 'Evet, martingale ve katmanlama stratejileri tek bir hesap içinde kullanılabilir. Ancak, bu stratejiler birden fazla hesapta kullanılmamalıdır.', 1654, 'tr', 40),
('Ist Martingale/Layering erlaubt?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ja, Martingale- und Layering-Strategien sind innerhalb eines einzelnen Kontos erlaubt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Diese Strategien dürfen jedoch nicht über mehrere Konten hinweg verwendet werden, um Manipulation oder Missbrauch der Strategien zu vermeiden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Das Öffnen desselben Paares über mehrere Konten ist nur unter den folgenden Bedingungen erlaubt:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Sie können eine Kaufposition auf XAUUSD in Konto A eröffnen und eine weitere Kaufposition auf XAUUSD in Konto B eröffnen, solange beide Positionen", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "innerhalb von 5 Minuten nacheinander eröffnet werden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ".", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn die Positionen nicht innerhalb von 5 Minuten nacheinander eröffnet werden, kann die Position in Konto B nur eröffnet werden, nachdem die Position in Konto A", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "vollständig geschlossen", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ".", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "Aufzählung", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wichtig:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Positionen im selben Paar über verschiedene Konten mehr als 5 Minuten auseinander eröffnet werden, sind alle Gewinne, die aus einer solchen Aktivität erzielt werden,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "auf allen beteiligten Konten", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "nicht für eine Auszahlung berechtigt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dieses Verhalten wird als sequenzielles Trading über Konten klassifiziert, was strengstens verboten ist.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "Aufzählung", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'ist-martingale-layering-erlaubt', 'Ist Martingale/Layering erlaubt?', 'Ja, Martingale- und Layering-Strategien sind innerhalb eines einzelnen Kontos erlaubt. Diese Strategien dürfen jedoch nicht über mehrere Konten hinweg verwendet werden, um zu vermeiden...', 1655, 'de', 40),
('هل يُسمح باستخدام مارتينجال/التدرج؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "نعم، استراتيجيات المارتينغال والتدرج مسموح بها ضمن حساب واحد.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "ومع ذلك، يجب عدم استخدام هذه الاستراتيجيات عبر حسابات متعددة لتجنب التلاعب أو إساءة استخدام الاستراتيجية.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "فتح نفس الزوج عبر حسابات متعددة مسموح به فقط تحت الشروط التالية:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "يمكنك فتح مركز شراء على XAUUSD في الحساب A وفتح مركز شراء آخر على XAUUSD في الحساب B، طالما أن كلا المركزين تم فتحهما", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "خلال 5 دقائق من بعضهما البعض", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ".", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا لم يتم فتح المركزين خلال 5 دقائق من بعضهما البعض، فيمكن فتح المركز في الحساب B فقط بعد أن يتم فتح المركز في الحساب A.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "مغلق بالكامل", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": ".", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "نقطة", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مهم:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا تم فتح مراكز على نفس الزوج عبر حسابات مختلفة بفارق أكثر من 5 دقائق، فإن أي ربح يتم تحقيقه من هذا النشاط", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "على جميع الحسابات المعنية", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "لن يكون مؤهلاً للدفع.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "يتم تصنيف هذا السلوك كتداول متسلسل عبر الحسابات، وهو محظور بشدة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "نقطة", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'يسمح بتطبيق طبقات مارتينجال', 'هل يُسمح باستخدام مارتينجال/التدرج؟', 'نعم، استراتيجيات المارتينغال والتدرج مسموح بها ضمن حساب واحد. ومع ذلك، يجب عدم استخدام هذه الاستراتيجيات عبر حسابات متعددة لتجنب...', 1656, 'ar', 40),
('Adakah Martingale/Layering dibenarkan?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ya, strategi martingale dan layering dibenarkan dalam satu akaun.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Walau bagaimanapun, strategi ini tidak boleh digunakan merentasi beberapa akaun untuk mengelakkan manipulasi atau penyalahgunaan strategi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Membuka pasangan yang sama merentasi beberapa akaun hanya dibenarkan di bawah syarat-syarat berikut:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Anda boleh membuka posisi Beli pada XAUUSD di Akaun A dan membuka posisi Beli lain pada XAUUSD di Akaun B, selagi kedua-dua posisi tersebut adalah", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "dibuka dalam masa 5 minit antara satu sama lain", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ".", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika posisi tersebut tidak dibuka dalam masa 5 minit antara satu sama lain, maka posisi di Akaun B hanya boleh dibuka selepas posisi di Akaun A telah", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "ditutup sepenuhnya", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ".", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "senarai", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Penting:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika posisi pada pasangan yang sama dibuka di pelbagai akaun lebih dari 5 minit berbeza, sebarang keuntungan yang dijana daripada aktiviti tersebut", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "pada semua akaun yang terlibat", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "tidak akan layak untuk pembayaran.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tingkah laku ini diklasifikasikan sebagai perdagangan berturutan di antara akaun, yang dilarang sama sekali.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "senarai", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'is-martingale-layering-allowed', 'Adakah Martingale/Layering dibenarkan?', 'Ya, strategi martingale dan pelapisan dibenarkan dalam satu akaun. Walau bagaimanapun, strategi ini tidak boleh digunakan merentasi beberapa akaun untuk mengelakkan...', 1657, 'ms', 40),
('How Does the Overall Drawdown Limit for the 1-Step NitroX Evaluation Work?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Overall Drawdown Limit for the 1-Step Nitro Evaluation is 3% from the Highest Recorded Balance", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Key Points to Understand:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ul", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Trailing Overall Drawdown:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " The Overall Drawdown is calculated based on your account’s Highest Balance (Maximum Balance Watermark) and does not reset daily at 5 PM EST. It consistently remains at 3% of the Account Size from the peak balance.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Fixed Drawdown After Profit", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": ": Once the account achieves a 3% profit, the Overall Drawdown Limit is fixed based on the Initial Account size, and the highest recorded balance no longer affects the limit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "bullet", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Start of Day 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Starting Balance/Equity: $100,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Initial Overall Drawdown: 3% of $100,000, which means the stop-out limit is set at $97,000. If Either Equity or Balance reaches this limit, it would result in a breach of the Overall Drawdown Limit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "During Day 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "New Balance: $102,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Overall Drawdown: 3% of $100,000 = $3,000, so the new stop-out limit is $102,000 – $3,000 = $99,000. If Either Equity or Balance reaches this limit, it would result in a breach of the Overall Drawdown Limit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Day 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Starting Balance/Equity: $101,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Allowed Overall Drawdown: The stop-out limit remains at $99,000 as it is based on the highest balance of $102,000. If Either Equity or Balance reaches this limit, it would result in a breach of the Overall Drawdown Limit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 2: After Achieving 3% Profit", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Day 3:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Starting Balance/Equity: $105,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Overall Drawdown: Fixed at $100,000 after achieving 3% profit (Overall Drawdown Limit becomes $100,000). If Either Equity or Balance reaches this limit, it would result in a breach of the Overall Drawdown Limit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'how-does-the-overall-drawdown-limit-for-the-1-step-nitrox-evaluation-work', 'How Does the Overall Drawdown Limit for the 1-Step NitroX Evaluation Work?', 'The Overall Drawdown Limit for the 1-Step Nitro Evaluation is 3% from the Highest Recorded Balance Key Points to Understand: Trailing Overall Drawdown:...', 1667, 'en