('Apakah Maksud Reset dan Bagaimana Ia Berfungsi pada Akaun Nitro X?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Reset pada akaun Nitro X membolehkan seorang pedagang yang telah melanggar akaun mereka (contohnya, dengan melebihi Had Kerugian Harian atau Keseluruhan) untuk mengembalikan akaun kepada baki asalnya pada masa pembelian dan memulakan semula.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda mempunyai akaun $100,000 dan melanggar Had Penarikan Harian 3%, anda boleh menetapkan semula akaun melalui Papan Pemuka anda dengan bayaran.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Setelah diset semula, akaun kembali kepada baki awal $100,000, dan anda boleh meneruskan perdagangan di bawah peraturan dan parameter risiko yang sama.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Kemaskini Penting mengenai Reset:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Reset Nitro X beroperasi pada kitaran tetap 30 hari yang bermula pada tarikh pembelian pertama akaun anda:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam tempoh 30 hari tersebut, anda boleh mereset akaun anda sebanyak mana yang anda mahu pada harga reset yang diskaun.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Selepas kitaran 30 hari berakhir, reset tidak lagi tersedia.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk mendapatkan semula akses kepada reset, anda mesti membeli semula Nitro X pada harga penuh, yang memulakan kitaran baru selama 30 hari.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'apa-itu-reset-dan-bagaimana-fungsinya-pada-akaun-nitro-x', 'Apakah Maksud Reset dan Bagaimana Ia Berfungsi pada Akaun Nitro X?', 'Reset pada akaun Nitro X membolehkan seorang peniaga yang telah melanggar akaun mereka (contohnya, dengan melebihi Had Kerugian Harian atau Keseluruhan) untuk memulihkan a...', 1811, 'ms', 29),
('What Is an Activation Fee on Nitro X?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "An activation fee on Nitro X account is a one-time charge of only ", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "$125", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": " that traders need to pay after passing the evaluation phase to activate their Simulated Funded account.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "This fee helps cover administrative costs and ensures your account is set up to begin trading with simulated funds.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'what-is-an-activation-fee-on-nitro-x', 'What Is an Activation Fee on Nitro X?', 'An activation fee on Nitro X account is a one-time charge of only $125 that traders need to pay after passing the evaluation phase to activate their Sim...', 1821, 'en', 28),
