('كيف يعمل الحد الإجمالي للسحب لحساب التمويل الفوري بلس؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "حد السحب الإجمالي لحساب التمويل الفوري بلس هو 6% من أعلى رصيد مسجل.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "نقاط رئيسية يجب فهمها:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "السحب الإجمالي المتتالي: يتم حساب السحب الإجمالي بناءً على أعلى رصيد لحسابك (علامة أقصى رصيد) ولا يتم إعادة تعيينه يوميًا في الساعة 5 مساءً بتوقيت شرق الولايات المتحدة. يتتبع باستمرار بنسبة 6% من أعلى رصيد مسجل.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "سحب ثابت بعد الربح: بمجرد أن تحقق الحساب ربحًا بنسبة 6%، يتم تثبيت حد السحب الإجمالي بناءً على حجم الحساب الأولي، ولم يعد أعلى رصيد مسجل يؤثر على الحد.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "نقطة", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "بداية اليوم الأول:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الرصيد/الملكية الابتدائية: 100,000 دولار", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "السحب الكلي الأولي: 6% من $100,000، مما يعني أن حد التوقف تم تعيينه عند $94,000. إذا وصلت أي من الأسهم أو الرصيد إلى هذا الحد، فسيؤدي ذلك إلى انتهاك حد السحب الكلي.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "خلال اليوم الأول:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الرصيد الجديد: 103,000 دولار", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "السحب الكلي: $103,000 – (6% من $100,000 = $6,000)، لذا فإن حد التوقف الجديد هو $97,000. إذا وصلت أي من الأسهم أو الرصيد إلى هذا الحد، فسيؤدي ذلك إلى انتهاك حد السحب الكلي.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "اليوم ٢:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "رصيد البداية / حقوق الملكية: 101,000 دولار", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "السحب الإجمالي المسموح به: يظل حد التوقف عند 97,000 دولار لأنه يعتمد على أعلى رصيد وهو 103,000 دولار. إذا وصل أي من حقوق الملكية أو الرصيد إلى هذا الحد، فسوف يؤدي ذلك إلى خرق حد السحب الإجمالي.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال 2: بعد تحقيق ربح بنسبة 6%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "اليوم 3:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الرصيد/الملكية الابتدائية: ١٠٦,٠٠٠ دولار", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "السحب الكلي: ثابت عند 100,000 دولار بعد تحقيق ربح بنسبة 6% (يصبح حد السحب الكلي 100,000 دولار). إذا وصلت إما الأسهم أو الرصيد إلى هذا الحد، فسيؤدي ذلك إلى خرق حد السحب الكلي.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'كيف يعمل الحد الإجمالي للسحب لحساب التمويل الفوري بلس؟', 'كيف يعمل الحد الإجمالي للسحب لحساب التمويل الفوري بلس؟', 'حد السحب الإجمالي لحساب التمويل الفوري بلس هو 6% من أعلى رصيد مسجل. النقاط الرئيسية لفهمها: سحب إجمالي متأخر...', 1983, 'ar', 16),
('Bagaimana Had Penarikan Keseluruhan untuk Akaun Pembiayaan Segera Plus Berfungsi?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hadiah Penarikan Keseluruhan untuk Akaun Pembiayaan Segera Plus adalah 6% dari Baki Tertinggi yang Direkodkan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Titik Utama untuk Difahami:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Penarikan Keseluruhan Tertinggal: Penarikan Keseluruhan dikira berdasarkan Baki Tertinggi akaun anda (Tanda Air Baki Maksimum) dan tidak diset semula setiap hari pada pukul 5 petang EST. Ia secara konsisten tertinggal pada 6% dari Baki Tertinggi yang Direkodkan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengeluaran Tetap Selepas Keuntungan: Setelah akaun mencapai keuntungan 6%, Had Pengeluaran Keseluruhan ditetapkan berdasarkan saiz Akaun Awal, dan baki tertinggi yang direkodkan tidak lagi mempengaruhi had tersebut.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "senarai", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Permulaan Hari 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Baki/Equiti Permulaan: $100,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengeluaran Keseluruhan Awal: 6% daripada $100,000, yang bermaksud had stop-out ditetapkan pada $94,000. Jika Mana-mana Ekuiti atau Baki mencapai had ini, ia akan mengakibatkan pelanggaran Had Pengeluaran Keseluruhan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pada Hari 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Baki Baru: $103,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengeluaran Keseluruhan: $103,000 – (6% daripada $100,000 = $6,000), jadi had stop-out baru adalah $97,000. Jika Mana-mana Ekuiti atau Baki mencapai had ini, ia akan mengakibatkan pelanggaran Had Pengeluaran Keseluruhan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hari 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Baki Permulaan/Ekuiti: $101,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hadiah Penarikan Keseluruhan: Had berhenti keluar kekal pada $97,000 kerana ia berdasarkan baki tertinggi sebanyak $103,000. Jika Sama ada Ekuiti atau Baki mencapai had ini, ia akan mengakibatkan pelanggaran Had Penarikan Keseluruhan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 2: Selepas Mencapai Keuntungan 6%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hari 3:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Baki/Equiti Permulaan: $106,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengurangan Keseluruhan: Tetap pada $100,000 setelah mencapai keuntungan 6% (Had Pengurangan Keseluruhan menjadi $100,000). Jika Sama ada Ekuiti atau Baki mencapai had ini, ia akan mengakibatkan pelanggaran Had Pengurangan Keseluruhan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'bagaimana-had-penarikan-keseluruhan-untuk-akaun-pembiayaan-segera-plus-berfungsi', 'Bagaimana Had Penarikan Keseluruhan untuk Akaun Pembiayaan Segera Plus Berfungsi?', 'Had Limit Penarikan Keseluruhan untuk Akaun Pembiayaan Segera Plus adalah 6% daripada Baki Tertinggi yang Direkodkan. Titik Utama untuk Difahami: Penarikan Keseluruhan yang Mengikut...', 1984, 'ms', 16),
('How Does the Maximum Daily Drawdown Limit for the Instant Funding Plus Account Work?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Maximum Daily Drawdown Limit is 3% of the Initial Balance.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "For a $100,000 Instant Funding Plus Account, the Daily Drawdown is 3% of the Initial Balance.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Day 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Starting Balance/Equity: $100,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Allowed Daily Drawdown: 3% of $100,000 = $3,000 (stop-out limit = $97,000)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Day 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "End of Day Balance (Day 1): $104,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "End of Day Equity (Day 1): $103,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "At 5 PM EST, if unrealised positions are open, then 3% of Initial balance will be deducted from the higher of the two. In Example 2 above since balance is higher than Equity, the stop out limit will become ($104,000 – (3% of 100,000)) = $104,000 – $3,000 = $101,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If either Equity or Balance reaches this limit, it would result in a breach of the Daily Drawdown Limit.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'how-does-the-maximum-daily-drawdown-limit-for-the-instant-funding-plus-account-work', 'How Does the Maximum Daily Drawdown Limit for the Instant Funding Plus Account Work?', 'The Maximum Daily Drawdown Limit is 3% of the Initial Balance. Example 1:For a $100,000 Instant Funding Plus Account, the Daily Drawdown is 3% of the In...', 1994, 'en', 15),
('Anında Fonlama Artı Hesabı için Maksimum Günlük Çekim Limiti Nasıl Çalışır?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Maksimum Günlük Çekilme Limiti, Başlangıç Bakiyesinin %3''üdür.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "$100,000 Anlık Fonlama Artı Hesabı için Günlük Çekim, Başlangıç Bakiyesinin %3''üdür.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "1. Gün:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Başlangıç Bakiyesi/Özsermaye: $100,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Günlük İzin Verilen Çekim: $100,000''ın %3''ü = $3,000 (stop-out limiti = $97,000)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "2. Gün:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Günün Sonundaki Bakiye (1. Gün): $104,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Günün Sonu Sermayesi (1. Gün): $103,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "EST saat 17:00''de, eğer gerçekleşmemiş pozisyonlar açıksa, o zaman başlangıç bakiyesinin %3''ü ikisinden yüksek olanından düşülecektir. Yukarıdaki Örnek 2''de, bakiye, Özsermaye''den yüksek olduğu için, stop out limiti ($104,000 – (100,000''in %3''ü)) = $104,000 – $3,000 = $101,000 olacaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer ya Özsermaye ya da Bakiye bu limite ulaşırsa, bu Günlük Çekilme Limiti''nin ihlaline neden olacaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'anlık-fonlama-artı-hesabı-için-maksimum-günlük-çekim-sınırı-nasıl-çalışır', 'Anında Fonlama Artı Hesabı için Maksimum Günlük Çekim Limiti Nasıl Çalışır?', 'Maksimum Günlük Çekilme Limiti, Başlangıç Bakiyesinin %3''üdür. Örnek 1: $100,000 Anlık Fonlama Artı Hesabı için, Günlük Çekilme Başlangıç Bakiyesinin %3''üdür.', 1995, 'tr', 15),
('Wie funktioniert das maximale tägliche Drawdown-Limit für das Instant Funding Plus-Konto?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Die maximale tägliche Drawdown-Grenze beträgt 3 % des Anfangsbalancs.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Für ein $100.000 Instant Funding Plus-Konto beträgt der tägliche Abbau 3 % des Anfangsguthabens.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tag 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Startguthaben/Eigenkapital: 100.000 $", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Erlaubter täglicher Drawdown: 3 % von $100.000 = $3.000 (Stop-Out-Grenze = $97.000)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Tag 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Endsaldo (Tag 1): $104.000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Ende des Tages Eigenkapital (Tag 1): $103.000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Um 17:00 Uhr EST, wenn nicht realisierte Positionen offen sind, werden 3 % des ursprünglichen Kontostands von dem höheren der beiden abgezogen. In Beispiel 2 oben, da der Kontostand höher ist als das Eigenkapital, wird die Stop-Out-Grenze ($104.000 – (3 % von 100.000)) = $104.000 – $3.000 = $101.000.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn entweder das Eigenkapital oder der Kontostand diese Grenze erreicht, führt dies zu einem Verstoß gegen die tägliche Drawdown-Grenze.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'wie-funktioniert-das-maximale-tägliche-drawdown-limit-für-das-instant-funding-plus-konto', 'Wie funktioniert das maximale tägliche Drawdown-Limit für das Instant Funding Plus-Konto?', 'Das maximale tägliche Drawdown-Limit beträgt 3 % des ursprünglichen Guthabens. Beispiel 1: Bei einem Instant Funding Plus-Konto von 100.000 $ beträgt der tägliche Drawdown 3 % des In...', 1996, 'de', 15),
('كيف يعمل الحد الأقصى اليومي للسحب لحساب التمويل الفوري بلس؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "حد السحب اليومي الأقصى هو 3% من الرصيد الأولي.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "لحساب تمويل فوري بلس بقيمة 100,000 دولار، فإن السحب اليومي هو 3% من الرصيد الابتدائي.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "اليوم 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الرصيد/الملكية الابتدائية: 100,000 دولار", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الحد اليومي المسموح به: 3% من $100,000 = $3,000 (حد التوقف = $97,000)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "اليوم ٢:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "رصيد نهاية اليوم (اليوم 1): $104,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"ty