('Bagaimana Had Penarikan Harian Maksimum untuk Akaun Pembiayaan Segera Plus Berfungsi?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Had maksimum pengeluaran harian adalah 3% daripada baki awal.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk Akaun Pembiayaan Segera Plus $100,000, Pengeluaran Harian adalah 3% daripada Baki Awal.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Hari 1:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Baki/Equiti Permulaan: $100,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengeluaran Harian yang Dibenarkan: 3% daripada $100,000 = $3,000 (had berhenti = $97,000)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hari 2:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Baki Akhir Hari (Hari 1): $104,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Akhir Hari Ekuiti (Hari 1): $103,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pada pukul 5 PM EST, jika posisi yang belum direalisasikan terbuka, maka 3% daripada baki Awal akan ditolak dari yang lebih tinggi antara kedua-duanya. Dalam Contoh 2 di atas, kerana baki lebih tinggi daripada Ekuiti, had stop out akan menjadi ($104,000 – (3% daripada 100,000)) = $104,000 – $3,000 = $101,000", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika sama ada Ekuiti atau Baki mencapai had ini, ia akan mengakibatkan pelanggaran Had Penarikan Harian.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'bagaimana had pengeluaran harian maksimum untuk akaun pembiayaan segera plus berfungsi', 'Bagaimana Had Penarikan Harian Maksimum untuk Akaun Pembiayaan Segera Plus Berfungsi?', 'Had Harian Penarikan Maksimum adalah 3% daripada Baki Awal. Contoh 1: Untuk Akaun Pembiayaan Segera Plus $100,000, Penarikan Harian adalah 3% daripada In...', 1998, 'ms', 15),
('Is There A Maximum Risk Rule On Instant Plus Accounts?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Instant Funding Plus Account is designed to reward disciplined traders with one of the highest payout structures in the industry, starting with an 80/20 profit split (80% to the trader, 20% to the firm).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "To maintain this split, traders must follow the FTM Shield Risk Protocol, a safeguard that ensures consistent, responsible risk management.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Key Rule: Floating Equity Loss ≤ 1%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "At no point can your account’s floating equity loss (unrealized losses from open positions) exceed 1% of your account balance.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ul", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If you are trading a $100,000 Instant Funding Plus account, your floating loss may never exceed $1,000.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If you are trading a $50,000 account, the maximum floating loss allowed is $500.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "bullet", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If your account breaches this threshold:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ol", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "All trades will automatically close.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Your profit split will adjust downward.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "number", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Profit Split Adjustments", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Violations of the Shield Protocol are tracked and penalized progressively:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ul", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "First violation → Split reduced to 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Second violation → Split reduced to 40/60", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Third violation → Split reduced to 30/70", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 4, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Fourth violation → Permanently locked at 20/80", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "bullet", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "This system encourages traders to preserve capital and avoid reckless drawdowns.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Practical Examples", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 1: Staying Within the Shield", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "You open a 5-lot position on EURUSD in a $100,000 account. Price moves against you and you are floating –$800. Since $800 is less than 1% ($1,000), you remain compliant. If the trade recovers or you close it, no penalty is triggered.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 2: Breaching the Shield Once", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "You open a gold (XAUUSD) position in a $100,000 account. Price quickly moves against you, and your floating loss hits –$1,200. This is above the $1,000 allowed. The system closes your trade, and your profit split is reduced from 80/20 to 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 3: Multiple Violations", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "First violation: floating loss hit $1,500 → Split reduced to 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Second violation: floating loss hit $2,000 → Split reduced to 40/60.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Third violation: floating loss hit $1,100 → Split reduced to 30/70.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Fourth violation: floating loss hit $1,300 → Split permanently locked at 20/80.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "At this point, no matter how long you trade successfully, you cannot regain a higher profit split.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Why This Matters", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "The Shield Rule exists to encourage responsible trading habits, prevent catastrophic losses from oversized positions, and reward consistency and discipline with the best possible payout. By respecting the 1% floating loss rule, traders not only protect their capital but also preserve their right to earn the maximum profit share.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Summary", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ul", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Maximum floating loss = 1% of account balance", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Breach it once = 80/20 drops to 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Breach it repeatedly = payout share reduces permanently", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "bullet", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Stay disciplined, respect the Shield, and enjoy 80% payouts as long as you manag