('Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Risiko Maksimum Pada Akaun Instant Plus?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Akaun Instant Funding Plus direka untuk memberi ganjaran kepada pedagang yang berdisiplin dengan salah satu struktur pembayaran tertinggi dalam industri, bermula dengan pembahagian keuntungan 80/20 (80% kepada pedagang, 20% kepada firma).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk mengekalkan pembahagian ini, pedagang mesti mengikuti Protokol Risiko FTM Shield, satu langkah berjaga-jaga yang memastikan pengurusan risiko yang konsisten dan bertanggungjawab.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Utama: Kerugian Ekuiti Terapung ≤ 1%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pada bila-bila masa, kerugian ekuiti terapung akaun anda (kerugian tidak direalisasikan dari posisi terbuka) tidak boleh melebihi 1% daripada baki akaun anda.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda sedang berdagang dengan akaun Instant Funding Plus bernilai $100,000, kerugian terapung anda tidak boleh melebihi $1,000.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda sedang berdagang dengan akaun bernilai $50,000, kerugian terapung maksimum yang dibenarkan adalah $500.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "senarai", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika akaun anda melepasi ambang ini:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ol", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Semua perdagangan akan ditutup secara automatik.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pembahagian keuntungan anda akan disesuaikan ke bawah.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "number", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Penyesuaian Pembahagian Keuntungan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran Protokol Perisai akan dipantau dan dihukum secara berperingkat:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran pertama → Bahagian dikurangkan kepada 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran kedua → Bahagian dikurangkan kepada 40/60", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran ketiga → Pembahagian dikurangkan kepada 30/70", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 4, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran keempat → Terkunci secara tetap pada 20/80", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "senarai", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Sistem ini menggalakkan peniaga untuk memelihara modal dan mengelakkan penarikan yang tidak berhemah.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh Praktikal", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 1: Kekal Dalam Perisai", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Anda membuka posisi 5-lot pada EURUSD dalam akaun $100,000. Harga bergerak menentang anda dan anda mengalami kerugian terapung –$800. Oleh kerana $800 adalah kurang daripada 1% ($1,000), anda tetap mematuhi. Jika perdagangan pulih atau anda menutupnya, tiada penalti yang dikenakan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 2: Melanggar Perisai Sekali", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Anda membuka posisi emas (XAUUSD) dalam akaun $100,000. Harga dengan cepat bergerak menentang anda, dan kerugian terapung anda mencapai –$1,200. Ini melebihi $1,000 yang dibenarkan. Sistem menutup perdagangan anda, dan pembahagian keuntungan anda dikurangkan dari 80/20 kepada 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 3: Pelanggaran Berganda", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran pertama: kerugian terapung mencapai $1,500 → Pembahagian dikurangkan kepada 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran kedua: kerugian terapung mencapai $2,000 → Pembahagian dikurangkan kepada 40/60.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran ketiga: kerugian terapung mencapai $1,100 → Pembahagian dikurangkan kepada 30/70.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran keempat: kerugian terapung mencapai $1,300 → Pembahagian terkunci secara tetap pada 20/80.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pada ketika ini, tidak kira berapa lama anda berdagang dengan berjaya, anda tidak dapat mendapatkan semula pembahagian keuntungan yang lebih tinggi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Mengapa Ini Penting", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Perisai wujud untuk menggalakkan tabiat perdagangan yang bertanggungjawab, mencegah kerugian bencana daripada posisi yang terlalu besar, dan menghargai konsistensi dan disiplin dengan pembayaran terbaik yang mungkin. Dengan menghormati peraturan kerugian terapung 1%, pedagang bukan sahaja melindungi modal mereka tetapi juga memelihara hak mereka untuk memperoleh bahagian keuntungan maksimum.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ringkasan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 1, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ul>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Kerugian terapung maksimum = 1% daripada baki akaun", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Melanggarnya sekali = 80/20 jatuh kepada 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 3, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Melanggar secara berulang = bahagian pembayaran berkurang secara kekal", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "senarai", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tetap berdisiplin, hormati Perisai, dan nikmati pembayaran 80% selagi anda menguruskan risiko anda dengan betul.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'adakah terdapat peraturan risiko maksimum pada akaun instant plus', 'Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Risiko Maksimum Pada Akaun Instant Plus?', 'Akaun Instant Funding Plus direka untuk memberi ganjaran kepada pedagang yang berdisiplin dengan salah satu struktur pembayaran tertinggi dalam industri, bermula dengan 8...', 2012, 'ms', 14),
