('Gibt es eine Regel zur Konsistenz für 2-Schritt-Plus-Konten?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Für 2-Step Plus-Konten gibt es in der Bewertungsphase keine Konsistenzregel. Die Konsistenzregel gilt nur für die finanzierte Phase.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Warum diese Regel?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Die Konsistenzregel der finanzierten Trader-Märkte fördert ein stetiges Gewinnwachstum und hilft Tradern, emotionales Trading zu vermeiden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wichtige Details zur Konsistenzregel für 2-Step Plus-Konten", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "In der Bewertungsphase gibt es keine Anforderung an Konsistenzregeln.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "In der finanzierten Phase sollten Sie nicht mehr als 45 % des Gesamtgewinns an einem Tag erzielt haben.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn der Gewinn eines einzelnen Tages mehr als 45 % Ihres Gesamtgewinns in der finanzierten Phase beträgt, müssen Sie mit dem Handel fortfahren, bis es keinen Tag mehr gibt, an dem der Gewinn über dem oben genannten Maximum liegt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wann ist die Konsistenzregel erforderlich?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Für 2-Step Plus-Konten gilt dies nur in der finanzierten Phase.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Berechnung", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "[Bester Tag % des Gesamtnutzens] = [Bester Tag Gewinn] ÷ [Gesamtgewinn] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Der beste Tagesgewinn bedeutet den höchsten Gewinn an einem einzelnen Tag.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Gewinn eines einzelnen Tages = Kontostand um 17 Uhr EST heute – Kontostand um 17 Uhr EST gestern", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel (2-Step Plus-Konto – Finanzierungsphase)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Sie in der Finanzierungsphase einen Gesamtnutzen von 10.000 $ erzielt haben,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Um für eine Auszahlung berechtigt zu sein, darf es keinen einzigen Tag gegeben haben, an dem mehr als 45 % von 10.000 $ (= 4.500 $) überschritten wurden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn es einen einzigen Tag mit mehr als 45 % des Gesamtgewinns gibt, müssen Sie weiterhin handeln, bis der Gewinn des besten Tages weniger als 45 % des Gesamtgewinns beträgt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'gibt-es-eine-regel-fuer-die-konsistenz-bei-2-schritt-plus-konten', 'Gibt es eine Regel zur Konsistenz für 2-Schritt-Plus-Konten?', 'Für 2-Step Plus-Konten gibt es in der Evaluierungsphase keine Konsistenzregel. Die Konsistenzregel gilt nur für die finanzierte Phase. Warum diese Regel?', 2080, 'de', 9),
('هل هناك قاعدة تتعلق بالاتساق لحسابات 2-Step Plus؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "بالنسبة لحسابات 2-Step Plus، لا توجد قاعدة اتساق في مرحلة التقييم. تنطبق قاعدة الاتساق فقط على المرحلة الممولة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "لماذا هذا القانون؟", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تروج قاعدة الاتساق في أسواق المتداولين الممولين لنمو الأرباح المستمر وتساعد المتداولين على تجنب التداول العاطفي.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "تفاصيل هامة حول قاعدة الاتساق لحسابات 2-Step Plus", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "في مرحلة التقييم؛ لا توجد متطلبات لقواعد التناسق.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "في المرحلة الممولة؛ يجب ألا تكون قد حققت أكثر من 45% من إجمالي الربح في يوم واحد.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا كان ربح يوم واحد أكثر من 45% من إجمالي ربحك في المرحلة الممولة، يجب عليك الاستمرار في التداول حتى لا يكون هناك يوم يتجاوز الحد الأقصى المذكور أعلاه.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "متى تكون قاعدة الاتساق مطلوبة؟", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "بالنسبة لحسابات 2-Step Plus، ينطبق ذلك فقط في مرحلة التمويل.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "حساب", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "[أفضل يوم % من إجمالي الربح] = [أفضل يوم ربح] ÷ [إجمالي الربح] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "يعني أفضل ربح يوم أعلى ربح في يوم واحد.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "ربح يوم واحد = الرصيد عند الساعة 5 مساءً بتوقيت شرق الولايات المتحدة اليوم - الرصيد عند الساعة 5 مساءً بتوقيت شرق الولايات المتحدة أمس", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال (حساب 2-Step Plus – المرحلة الممولة)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا حققت ربحًا إجماليًا قدره 10,000 دولار في المرحلة الممولة،", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "لكي تكون مؤهلاً للسحب، يجب ألا يكون هناك يوم واحد تجاوز فيه الربح 45% من 10,000 دولار (= 4,500 دولار).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا كان هناك يوم واحد يحقق أكثر من 45% من إجمالي الربح، فعليك الاستمرار في التداول حتى يكون أفضل ربح يومي أقل من 45% من إجمالي الربح.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'هل هناك قاعدة تتعلق بالاتساق لحسابات 2-Step Plus؟', 'هل هناك قاعدة تتعلق بالاتساق لحسابات 2-Step Plus؟', 'بالنسبة لحسابات 2-Step Plus، لا توجد قاعدة اتساق في مرحلة التقييم. تنطبق قاعدة الاتساق فقط على المرحلة الممولة. لماذا هذه القاعدة؟ Fund...', 2081, 'ar', 9),
('Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Mengenai Konsistensi untuk Akaun 2-Step Plus?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun 2-Step Plus, tiada peraturan konsistensi dalam Fasa Penilaian. Peraturan konsistensi hanya terpakai untuk Fasa Dibiayai.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Mengapa Peraturan ini?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Konsistensi Pasaran Pedagang Berpendanaan mempromosikan pertumbuhan keuntungan yang stabil dan membantu pedagang mengelakkan perdagangan yang beremosi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Butiran Penting Mengenai Peraturan Konsistensi Untuk Akaun 2-Step Plus", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Penilaian; tiada keperluan peraturan konsistensi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Dibiayai; anda tidak seharusnya memperoleh lebih daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan dalam satu hari.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika keuntungan dalam satu hari melebihi 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan anda dalam Fasa Dibiayai, anda perlu meneruskan perdagangan sehingga tiada hari yang melebihi maksimum yang dinyatakan di atas.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bilakah Peraturan Konsistensi Diperlukan?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk akaun 2-Step Plus, ia hanya terpakai dalam Fasa Dibiayai.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pengiraan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "[Hari Terbaik % daripada Jumlah Keuntungan] = [Keuntungan Hari Terbaik] ÷ [Jumlah Keuntungan] * 100", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Keuntungan Hari Terbaik bermaksud keuntungan hari tunggal tertinggi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Keuntungan Hari Tunggal = Baki pada 5pm EST Hari Ini – Baki pada 5pm EST Semalam", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh (Akaun 2-Langkah Plus – Fasa Dibiayai)", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda telah memperoleh keuntungan keseluruhan sebanyak $10,000 dalam Fasa Dibiayai,", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Untuk layak mengeluarkan wang, tidak boleh ada satu hari pun dengan lebih daripada 45% daripada $10,000 (= $4,500).", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika terdapat satu hari dengan lebih daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan, maka anda perlu terus berdagang sehingga keuntungan hari terbaik kurang daripada 45% daripada jumlah keuntungan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'adakah-peraturan-mengenai-konsistensi-untuk-akaun-2-langkah-plus', 'Adakah Terdapat Peraturan Mengenai Konsistensi untuk Akaun 2-Step Plus?', 'Untuk akaun 2-Step Plus, tiada peraturan konsistensi dalam Fasa Penilaian. Peraturan konsistensi hanya terpakai untuk Fasa Dibiayai. Mengapa Peraturan ini? Fund...', 2082, 'ms', 9),
