('Adakah Terdapat Keperluan Hari Perdagangan Minimum Untuk Akaun 2-Step Plus?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Cabaran, Ya, terdapat keperluan minimum 3 hari dagangan untuk lulus cabaran.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Dalam Fasa Dana Simulasi, Ya, terdapat keperluan minimum 5 hari dagangan untuk Akaun 2-Langkah Plus layak untuk pembayaran. Sila ambil perhatian bahawa hari dagangan dicapai jika sekurang-kurangnya 0.5% keuntungan direkodkan pada hari itu.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'adakah terdapat keperluan hari perdagangan minimum untuk akaun 2 langkah plus', 'Adakah Terdapat Keperluan Hari Perdagangan Minimum Untuk Akaun 2-Step Plus?', 'Dalam Fasa Cabaran, Ya, terdapat keperluan minimum 3 hari perdagangan untuk lulus cabaran. Dalam Fasa Dana Simulasi, Ya, terdapat minimum...', 2171, 'ms', 2),
('Is there a Maximum Risk Rule On 2-Step Plus Accounts?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The 2-Step Plus Account is designed to reward disciplined traders with one of the highest payout structures in the industry, starting with an 80/20 profit split (80% to the trader, 20% to the firm). To maintain this split, traders must follow the FTM Shield Risk Protocol, a safeguard that ensures consistent, responsible risk management.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "The Key Rule: Floating Equity Loss ≤ 1.5%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "At no point can your account’s floating equity loss (unrealized losses from open positions) exceed 1.5% of your account balance.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "If you are trading a $100,000 2-Step Plus account, your floating loss may never exceed $1,500.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "If you are trading a $50,000 account, the maximum floating loss allowed is $750.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "If your account breaches this threshold:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ol", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "All trades will automatically close.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Your profit split will adjust downward.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "number", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Profit Split Adjustments", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Violations of the Shield Protocol are tracked and penalized progressively:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "First violation → Split reduced to 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Second violation → Split reduced to 40/60", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Third violation → Split reduced to 30/70", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Fourth violation → Permanently locked at 20/80", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "This system encourages traders to preserve capital and avoid reckless drawdowns.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Practical Examples", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 1: Staying Within the Shield", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "You open a 5-lot position on EURUSD in a $100,000 account. Price moves against you and you are floating –$1,200. Since $1,200 is less than 1.5% ($1,500), you remain compliant. If the trade recovers or you close it, no penalty is triggered.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 2: Breaching the Shield Once", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "You open a gold (XAUUSD) position in a $100,000 account. Price quickly moves against you, and your floating loss hits –$1,700. This is above the $1,500 allowed. The system closes your trade, and your profit split is reduced from 80/20 to 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Example 3: Multiple Violations", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "First violation: floating loss hit $1,600 → Split reduced to 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Second violation: floating loss hit $2,000 → Split reduced to 40/60.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Third violation: floating loss hit $1,800 → Split reduced to 30/70.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Fourth violation: floating loss hit $1,900 → Split permanently locked at 20/80.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "At this point, no matter how long you trade successfully, you cannot regain a higher profit split.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Why This Matters?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "The Shield Rule exists to encourage responsible trading habits, prevent catastrophic losses from oversized positions, and reward consistency and discipline with the best possible payout. By respecting the 1.5% floating loss rule, traders not only protect their capital but also preserve their right to earn the maximum profit share.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Summary:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Maximum floating loss = 1.5% of account balance", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Breach it once = 80/20 drops to 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Breach it repeatedly = payout share reduces permanently", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Stay disciplined, respect the Shield, and enjoy 80% payouts as long as you manage your risk correctly.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'is-there-a-maximum-risk-rule-on-2-step-plus-accounts', 'Is there a Maximum Risk Rule On 2-Step Plus Accounts?', 'The 2-Step Plus Account is designed to reward disciplined traders with one of the highest payout structures in the industry, starting with an 80/20 prof...', 2181, 'en', 1),
('2-Adım Artı Hesaplarda Maksimum Risk Kuralı Var mı?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "2-Adım Artı Hesabı, disiplinli yatırımcıları sektördeki en yüksek ödeme yapısı ile ödüllendirmek için tasarlanmıştır; bu, %80''lik bir kar paylaşımı ile başlar (yüzde 80 yatırımcıya, yüzde 20 firmaya). Bu paylaşımı korumak için yatırımcıların FTM Shield Risk Protokolü''ne uyması gerekmektedir; bu, tutarlı ve sorumlu risk yönetimini sağlamak için bir güvenlik önlemidir.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ana Kural: Sürekli Sermaye Kaybı ≤ %1.5", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Hiçbir durumda hesabınızdaki sürekli sermaye kaybı (açık pozisyonlardan kaynaklanan gerçekleşmemiş kayıplar) hesap bakiyenizin %1.5''ini aşamaz.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer 100.000 $ değerinde bir 2-Adım Artı hesabı ile işlem yapıyorsanız, sürekli kaybınız asla 1.500 $''ı aşamaz.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "$50,000''lık bir hesapla işlem yapıyorsanız, izin verilen maksimum açık kayıp $750''dır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Eğer hesabınız bu eşiği aşarsa:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ol", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tüm işlemler otomatik olarak kapanacaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Kar payınız aşağı yönde ayarlanacaktır.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "number", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Kar Payı Ayarlamaları", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Kalkan Protokolü ihlalleri izlenir ve kademeli olarak cezalandırılır:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "İlk ihlal → Pay %50/%50''ye düşürülür", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "İkinci ihlal → Pay %40/%60''a düşürülür", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Üçüncü ihlal → Pay 30/70''e düşürüldü", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Dördüncü ihlal → Süresiz olarak 20/80''de kilitlendi", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu sistem, yatırımcıları sermayelerini korumaya ve dikkatsiz düşüşlerden kaçınmaya teşvik eder.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pratik Örnekler", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek 1: Kalkan İçinde Kalmak", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "EURUSD''de 100.000 $''lık bir hesapla 5 lotluk bir pozisyon açıyorsunuz. Fiyat size karşı hareket ediyor ve -1.200 $''da kalıyorsunuz. 1.200 $ 1,5%''ten ($1.500) az olduğu için uyumlu kalıyorsunuz. Eğer işlem toparlanırsa veya kapatırsanız, herhangi bir ceza tetiklenmez.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek 2: Kalkanı Bir Kez İhlal Etmek", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "$100,000''lık bir hesapta bir altın (XAUUSD) pozisyonu açıyorsunuz. Fiyat hızla aleyhinize hareket ediyor ve açık kaybınız –$1,700''e ulaşıyor. Bu, izin verilen $1,500''ün üzerinde. Sistem işleminizi kapatıyor ve kar payınız %80/%20''den %50/%50''ye düşüyor.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Örnek 3: Birden Fazla İhlal", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "İlk ihlal: açık kayıp $1,600''e ulaştı → Pay %50/%50''ye düşürüldü.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "İkinci ihlal: açık kayıp $2,000''e ulaştı → Pay 40/60''a düşürüldü.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Üçüncü ihlal: kayıp $1,800''e ulaştı → Pay 30/70''e düşürüldü.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Dördüncü ihlal: kayıp $1,900''a ulaştı → Pay kalıcı olarak 20/80''de kilitlendi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu noktada, ne kadar uzun süre başarılı bir şekilde ticaret yaparsanız yapın, daha yüksek bir kâr payını geri kazanamazsınız.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bu Neden Önemli?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Kalkan Kuralı, sorumlu ticaret alışkanlıklarını teşvik etmek, aşırı pozisyonlardan kaynaklanan felaket kayıplarını önlemek ve en iyi ödeme ile tutarlılık ve disiplini ödüllendirmek için vardır. %1.5''lik dalgalı kayıp kuralına saygı göstererek, traderlar sadece sermayelerini korumakla kalmaz, aynı zamanda maksimum kar payını kazanma haklarını da korurlar.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Özet:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Maksimum dalgalı kayıp = Hesap bakiyesinin %1.5''i", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Bir kez ihlal edilirse = 80/20, 50/50''ye düşer", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Tekrar tekrar ihlal etmek = ödeme payı kalıcı olarak azalır", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Disiplinli kalın, Kalkan''a saygı gösterin ve riskinizi doğru bir şekilde yönetmeniz koşuluyla %80 ödeme almanın tadını çıkarın.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', '2 adım artı hesaplarda maksimum risk kuralı var mı?', '2-Adım Artı Hesaplarda Maksimum Risk Kuralı Var mı?', '2-Adım Artı Hesabı, disiplinli yatırımcıları sektördeki en yüksek ödeme yapısı ile ödüllendirmek için tasarlanmıştır; %80/%20 kâr ile başlayarak...', 2182, 'tr', 1),
('Gibt es eine maximale Risikoregel für 2-Step Plus-Konten?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Das 2-Step Plus-Konto ist darauf ausgelegt, disziplinierte Trader mit einer der höchsten Auszahlungsstrukturen der Branche zu belohnen, beginnend mit einer Gewinnaufteilung von 80/20 (80 % für den Trader, 20 % für die Firma). Um diese Aufteilung aufrechtzuerhalten, müssen Trader das FTM Shield Risk Protocol befolgen, eine Sicherheitsmaßnahme, die ein konsistentes und verantwortungsvolles Risikomanagement gewährleistet.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Die Hauptregel: Schwankende Eigenkapitalverluste ≤ 1,5 %", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Zu keinem Zeitpunkt darf der schwankende Eigenkapitalverlust Ihres Kontos (nicht realisierte Verluste aus offenen Positionen) 1,5 % Ihres Kontostands überschreiten.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Sie ein 2-Step Plus-Konto mit 100.000 $ handeln, darf Ihr schwankender Verlust 1.500 $ niemals überschreiten.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Sie ein Konto von 50.000 $ handeln, beträgt der maximal zulässige schwebende Verlust 750 $.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Wenn Ihr Konto diese Schwelle überschreitet:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ol", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Alle Trades werden automatisch geschlossen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ihre Gewinnaufteilung wird nach unten angepasst.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "number", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Anpassungen der Gewinnaufteilung", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Verstöße gegen das Shield-Protokoll werden verfolgt und progressiv bestraft:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Erster Verstoß → Anteil auf 50/50 reduziert", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Zweiter Verstoß → Anteil auf 40/60 reduziert", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Dritte Verletzung → Aufteilung auf 30/70 reduziert", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Vierte Verletzung → Dauerhaft auf 20/80 gesperrt", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Dieses System ermutigt Händler, Kapital zu erhalten und riskante Rückgänge zu vermeiden.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Praktische Beispiele", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel 1: Innerhalb des Schutzschilds bleiben", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Sie eröffnen eine 5-Lot-Position auf EURUSD in einem Konto von 100.000 $. Der Preis bewegt sich gegen Sie und Sie haben einen unrealisierten Verlust von -1.200 $. Da -1.200 $ weniger als 1,5 % (1.500 $) sind, bleiben Sie konform. Wenn der Trade sich erholt oder Sie ihn schließen, wird keine Strafe ausgelöst.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel 2: Den Schutzschild einmal verletzen", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Sie eröffnen eine Goldposition (XAUUSD) in einem Konto von 100.000 $. Der Preis bewegt sich schnell gegen Sie, und Ihr schwimmender Verlust erreicht -1.700 $. Dies liegt über den erlaubten 1.500 $. Das System schließt Ihren Handel, und Ihre Gewinnaufteilung wird von 80/20 auf 50/50 reduziert.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Beispiel 3: Mehrfache Verstöße", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Erster Verstoß: schwimmender Verlust erreicht 1.600 $ → Aufteilung auf 50/50 reduziert.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Zweiter Verstoß: schwebender Verlust von 2.000 $ → Aufteilung auf 40/60 reduziert.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Dritte Verletzung: schwebender Verlust erreichte $1.800 → Aufteilung auf 30/70 reduziert.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Vierte Verletzung: schwebender Verlust erreichte $1.900 → Aufteilung dauerhaft auf 20/80 gesperrt.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "An diesem Punkt, egal wie lange Sie erfolgreich handeln, können Sie keinen höheren Gewinnanteil zurückgewinnen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Warum ist das wichtig?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Die Shield-Regel existiert, um verantwortungsvolle Handelsgewohnheiten zu fördern, katastrophale Verluste durch übergroße Positionen zu verhindern und Konsistenz sowie Disziplin mit der bestmöglichen Auszahlung zu belohnen. Durch die Einhaltung der Regel für einen schwebenden Verlust von 1,5 % schützen Trader nicht nur ihr Kapital, sondern bewahren sich auch das Recht, den maximalen Gewinnanteil zu erzielen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Zusammenfassung:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Maximaler schwebender Verlust = 1,5 % des Kontostands", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Einmalige Überschreitung = 80/20 sinkt auf 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Wiederholter Verstoß = Auszahlungsteil reduziert sich dauerhaft", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Bleiben Sie diszipliniert, respektieren Sie das Schild und genießen Sie 80% Auszahlungen, solange Sie Ihr Risiko korrekt managen.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'gibt-es-eine-maximalrisikoregel-für-2-step-plus-konten', 'Gibt es eine maximale Risikoregel für 2-Step Plus-Konten?', 'Das 2-Step Plus-Konto wurde entwickelt, um disziplinierte Händler mit einer der höchsten Auszahlungsstrukturen der Branche zu belohnen, beginnend mit einem 80/20-Profit...', 2183, 'de', 1),
('هل هناك قاعدة المخاطر القصوى على حسابات 2-Step Plus؟', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "تم تصميم حساب 2-Step Plus لمكافأة المتداولين المنضبطين بأحد أعلى هياكل العائدات في الصناعة، بدءًا من تقسيم الأرباح 80/20 (80% للمتداول، 20% للشركة). للحفاظ على هذا التقسيم، يجب على المتداولين اتباع بروتوكول مخاطر FTM Shield، وهو إجراء يضمن إدارة مخاطر مسؤولة ومتسقة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "القاعدة الأساسية: خسارة حقوق الملكية العائمة ≤ 1.5%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "لا يمكن أن تتجاوز خسارة حقوق الملكية العائمة في حسابك (الخسائر غير المحققة من المراكز المفتوحة) 1.5% من رصيد حسابك في أي وقت.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا كنت تتداول في حساب 2-Step Plus بقيمة 100,000 دولار، فلا يجوز أن تتجاوز خسارتك العائمة 1,500 دولار.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا كنت تتداول بحساب بقيمة 50,000 دولار، فإن الحد الأقصى للخسارة العائمة المسموح بها هو 750 دولار.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "إذا تجاوز حسابك هذا الحد:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "<ol>", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "سيتم إغلاق جميع الصفقات تلقائيًا.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "سيتم تعديل نسبة أرباحك نحو الأسفل.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "number", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "تعديلات نسبة الأرباح", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "يتم تتبع انتهاكات بروتوكول الدرع ومعاقبتها بشكل تدريجي:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الانتهاك الأول → يتم تقليل النسبة إلى 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الانتهاك الثاني → يتم تقليل النسبة إلى 40/60", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الانتهاك الثالث → تم تقليل الانقسام إلى 30/70", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الانتهاك الرابع → تم قفله بشكل دائم عند 20/80", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "يشجع هذا النظام المتداولين على الحفاظ على رأس المال وتجنب الانخفاضات المتهورة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "أمثلة عملية", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال 1: البقاء ضمن الدرع", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تفتح مركزًا بحجم 5 لوت على EURUSD في حساب بقيمة 100,000 دولار. يتحرك السعر ضدك وأنت عائم بمقدار -1,200 دولار. نظرًا لأن -1,200 دولار أقل من 1.5% (1,500 دولار)، فإنك تبقى متوافقًا. إذا تعافى التداول أو أغلقته، فلن يتم تفعيل أي عقوبة.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال 2: خرق الدرع مرة واحدة", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تفتح مركزًا في الذهب (XAUUSD) في حساب بقيمة 100,000 دولار. يتحرك السعر بسرعة ضدك، ويصل خسارتك العائمة إلى -1,700 دولار. هذا يتجاوز الحد المسموح به وهو 1,500 دولار. يقوم النظام بإغلاق صفقتك، ويتم تقليل نسبة أرباحك من 80/20 إلى 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "مثال 3: انتهاكات متعددة", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الانتهاك الأول: خسارة عائمة وصلت إلى 1,600 دولار → تم تقليل النسبة إلى 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الانتهاك الثاني: الخسارة العائمة بلغت 2,000 دولار → تم تقليل النسبة إلى 40/60.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الانتهاك الثالث: الخسارة العائمة وصلت إلى 1,800 دولار → تم تقليل النسبة إلى 30/70.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "الانتهاك الرابع: الخسارة العائمة وصلت إلى 1,900 دولار → تم قفل النسبة بشكل دائم عند 20/80.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "في هذه المرحلة، بغض النظر عن مدة تداولك بنجاح، لا يمكنك استعادة نسبة أرباح أعلى.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "لماذا هذا مهم؟", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "قاعدة الدرع موجودة لتشجيع عادات التداول المسؤولة، ومنع الخسائر الكارثية الناتجة عن المراكز الكبيرة، ومكافأة الاستمرارية والانضباط بأفضل عائد ممكن. من خلال احترام قاعدة الخسارة العائمة بنسبة 1.5%، لا يحمي المتداولون رأس مالهم فحسب، بل يحافظون أيضًا على حقهم في كسب أقصى حصة من الأرباح.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "ملخص:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "أقصى خسارة عائمة = 1.5% من رصيد الحساب", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "تجاوزها مرة واحدة = 80/20 ينخفض إلى 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "عادي", "text": "خرقها بشكل متكرر = حصة الدفع تقل بشكل دائم", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "عادي", "text": "ابقَ منضبطًا، واحترم الدرع، واستمتع بدفعات بنسبة 80% طالما أنك تدير مخاطر بشكل صحيح.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'هل هناك قاعدة مخاطر قصوى على حسابات 2-Step Plus؟', 'هل هناك قاعدة المخاطر القصوى على حسابات 2-Step Plus؟', 'تم تصميم حساب 2-Step Plus لمكافأة المتداولين المنضبطين بأحد أعلى هياكل العوائد في الصناعة، بدءًا من 80/20 ربح...', 2184, 'ar', 1),
('Adakah terdapat Peraturan Risiko Maksimum untuk Akaun 2-Step Plus?', '{"root": {"type": "root", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Akaun 2-Step Plus direka untuk memberi ganjaran kepada pedagang yang berdisiplin dengan salah satu struktur pembayaran tertinggi dalam industri, bermula dengan pembahagian keuntungan 80/20 (80% kepada pedagang, 20% kepada firma). Untuk mengekalkan pembahagian ini, pedagang mesti mengikuti Protokol Risiko FTM Shield, satu langkah berjaga-jaga yang memastikan pengurusan risiko yang konsisten dan bertanggungjawab.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Utama: Kerugian Ekuiti Terapung ≤ 1.5%", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pada bila-bila masa, kerugian ekuiti terapung akaun anda (kerugian tidak direalisasikan dari posisi terbuka) tidak boleh melebihi 1.5% daripada baki akaun anda.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda sedang berdagang dengan akaun 2-Step Plus bernilai $100,000, kerugian terapung anda tidak boleh melebihi $1,500.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika anda berdagang dengan akaun $50,000, kerugian terapung maksimum yang dibenarkan adalah $750.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Jika akaun anda melepasi ambang ini:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"tag": "ol", "type": "list", "start": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"type": "listitem", "value": 1, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Semua perdagangan akan ditutup secara automatik.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}, {"type": "listitem", "value": 2, "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pembahagian keuntungan anda akan disesuaikan ke bawah.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null}], "listType": "number", "direction": null}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Penyesuaian Pembahagian Keuntungan", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran Protokol Perisai akan dipantau dan dihukum secara berperingkat:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran pertama → Bahagian dikurangkan kepada 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran kedua → Bahagian dikurangkan kepada 40/60", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran ketiga → Pembahagian dikurangkan kepada 30/70", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran keempat → Terkunci secara tetap pada 20/80", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Sistem ini menggalakkan peniaga untuk memelihara modal dan mengelakkan penarikan yang tidak berhemah.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh Praktikal", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 1: Kekal Dalam Perisai", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Anda membuka posisi 5-lot pada EURUSD dalam akaun $100,000. Harga bergerak menentang anda dan anda mengalami kerugian terapung –$1,200. Oleh kerana $1,200 adalah kurang daripada 1.5% ($1,500), anda tetap mematuhi. Jika perdagangan pulih atau anda menutupnya, tiada penalti yang akan dikenakan.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 2: Melanggar Perisai Sekali", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Anda membuka posisi emas (XAUUSD) dalam akaun $100,000. Harga dengan cepat bergerak menentang anda, dan kerugian terapung anda mencapai –$1,700. Ini melebihi $1,500 yang dibenarkan. Sistem menutup perdagangan anda, dan pembahagian keuntungan anda dikurangkan dari 80/20 kepada 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Contoh 3: Pelanggaran Berganda", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran pertama: kerugian terapung mencapai $1,600 → Pembahagian dikurangkan kepada 50/50.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran kedua: kerugian terapung mencapai $2,000 → Pembahagian dikurangkan kepada 40/60.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran ketiga: kerugian terapung mencapai $1,800 → Pembahagian dikurangkan kepada 30/70.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Pelanggaran keempat: kerugian terapung mencapai $1,900 → Pembahagian terkunci secara tetap pada 20/80.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Pada ketika ini, tidak kira berapa lama anda berdagang dengan berjaya, anda tidak dapat mendapatkan semula pembahagian keuntungan yang lebih tinggi.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Mengapa Ini Penting?", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Peraturan Perisai wujud untuk menggalakkan tabiat perdagangan yang bertanggungjawab, mencegah kerugian bencana daripada posisi yang terlalu besar, dan memberi ganjaran kepada konsistensi dan disiplin dengan pembayaran yang terbaik. Dengan menghormati peraturan kerugian terapung 1.5%, pedagang bukan sahaja melindungi modal mereka tetapi juga memelihara hak mereka untuk memperoleh bahagian keuntungan maksimum.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Ringkasan:", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Kerugian terapung maksimum = 1.5% daripada baki akaun", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Melanggarnya sekali = 80/20 jatuh kepada 50/50", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}, {"type": "linebreak", "version": 1}, {"mode": "normal", "text": "Melanggar secara berulang = bahagian pembayaran berkurang secara kekal", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}, {"type": "paragraph", "format": "", "indent": 0, "version": 1, "children": [{"mode": "normal", "text": "Tetap berdisiplin, hormati Perisai, dan nikmati pembayaran 80% selagi anda menguruskan risiko anda dengan betul.", "type": "text", "style": "", "detail": 0, "format": 0, "version": 1}], "direction": null, "textStyle": "", "textFormat": 0}], "direction": null}}', 'adakah terdapat peraturan risiko maksimum untuk akaun 2-langkah-plus', 'Adakah terdapat Peraturan Risiko Maksimum untuk Akaun 2-Step Plus?', 'Akaun 2-Step Plus direka untuk memberi ganjaran kepada pedagang yang berdisiplin dengan salah satu struktur pembayaran tertinggi dalam industri, bermula dengan keuntungan 80/20...', 2185, 'ms', 1),
